#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:125
msgid ""
"Coordinate with vendors to deliver orders directly to customers, bypassing "
"internal stock"
msgstr ""
"Coördineer met leveranciers om orders rechtstreeks bij klanten af te "
"leveren, waarbij interne voorraad wordt overgeslagen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods.rst:5
msgid "Picking methods"
msgstr "Pickmethoden"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:130
msgid ""
"Optimize picking operations using piece, batch, cluster, or wave picking "
"techniques"
msgstr ""
"Optimaliseer pickactiviteiten met behulp van stuk-, batch-, cluster- of "
"golfpicktechnieken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:135
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:6
msgid "Removal strategies"
msgstr "Verwijderingsstrategieën"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:135
msgid ""
"Use FIFO, LIFO, or FEFO strategies to automate the selection of products for "
"delivery"
msgstr ""
"Gebruik FIFO-, LIFO- of FEFO-strategieën om de selectie van producten voor "
"levering te automatiseren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:141
msgid "Customization"
msgstr "Aanpassen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:143
msgid ""
"Odoo's flexible framework enables businesses to tailor workflows to match "
"specific operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Het flexibele framework van Odoo stelt bedrijven in staat om workflows aan "
"te passen aan specifieke operationele behoeften."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations.rst:148
msgid ""
"Define tailored receiving or delivery workflows to meet specific business "
"needs"
msgstr ""
"Definieer op maat gemaakte ontvangst- of leveringsworkflows om aan "
"specifieke bedrijfsbehoeften te voldoen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:3
msgid "Three-step delivery"
msgstr "Levering in drie stappen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:5
msgid ""
"Some companies process large amounts of deliveries every day, many of which "
"include multiple products or require special packaging. To make this "
"efficient, a packing step is needed before shipping out products. For this, "
"Odoo has a three step process for delivering goods."
msgstr ""
"Sommige bedrijven verwerken elke dag grote hoeveelheden leveringen, waarvan "
"er veel meerdere producten bevatten of speciale verpakking vereisen. Om dit "
"efficiënt te maken is een verpakkingsstap nodig voordat producten worden "
"verzonden. Hiervoor heeft Odoo een proces van drie stappen voor het leveren "
"van goederen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:9
msgid ""
"In the default three-step delivery process, products that are part of a "
"delivery order are picked in the warehouse according to their removal "
"strategy, and brought to a packing zone. After the items have been packed "
"into the different shipments in the packing zone, they are brought to an "
"output location before being shipped. These steps can be modified if they do "
"not fit the needs of the business."
msgstr ""
"In het standaard leveringsproces van drie stappen worden producten die deel "
"uitmaken van een leveringsorder gepickt in het magazijn volgens hun "
"verwijderstrategie, en naar een verpakkingszone gebracht. Nadat de artikelen "
"zijn verpakt in de verschillende zendingen in de verpakkingszone, worden ze "
"naar een uitvoerlocatie gebracht voordat ze worden verzonden. Deze stappen "
"kunnen worden aangepast als ze niet aan de behoeften van het bedrijf voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:18
msgid ""
"To change delivery settings from :doc:`one step "
"<receipts_delivery_one_step>` to three steps, make sure the *Multi-Step "
"Routes* option is enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration "
"--> Settings --> Warehouse`. Note that activating :guilabel:`Multi-Step "
"Routes` will also activate *Storage Locations*."
msgstr ""
"Om leveringsinstellingen te wijzigen van :doc:`één stap "
"<receipts_delivery_one_step>` naar drie stappen, zorg je ervoor dat de optie "
"*Routes met meerdere stappen* is ingeschakeld in :menuselection:`Voorraad "
"app --> Configuratie --> Instellingen --> Magazijn`. Let op: het activeren "
"van :guilabel:`Routes met meerdere stappen` activeert ook *Opslaglocaties*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Activate multi-step routes and storage locations in inventory settings."
msgstr ""
"Activeer routes met meerdere stappen en opslaglocaties in "
"voorraadinstellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:27
msgid ""
"Next, the warehouse needs to be configured for three step deliveries. To do "
"this, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, "
"and click on the :guilabel:`warehouse` to edit. Then, select :guilabel:`Pack "
"goods, send goods in output and then deliver (3 steps)` "
"for :guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments`."
msgstr ""
"Vervolgens moet het magazijn worden geconfigureerd voor leveringen in drie "
"stappen. Ga hiervoor naar :menuselection:`Voorraad app --> Configuratie --> "
"Magazijnen`, en klik op het :guilabel:`magazijn` om te bewerken. Selecteer "
"vervolgens :guilabel:`Verpak goederen, verzend goederen in uitvoer en lever "
"dan (3 stappen)` voor :guilabel:`Uitgaande zendingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Set outgoing shipment option to deliver in three steps."
msgstr ""
"Stel de optie voor uitgaande zendingen in om in drie stappen te leveren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:36
msgid ""
"Activating three-step receipts and deliveries creates two new internal "
"locations: a *Packing Zone* (WH/Packing Zone), and *Output* (WH/Output). To "
"rename these locations, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Locations`, click on the :guilabel:`Location` to change, "
"and update the name."
msgstr ""
"Het activeren van ontvangsten en leveringen in drie stappen creëert twee "
"nieuwe interne locaties: een *Verpakkingszone* (WH/Packing Zone) en "
"*Uitvoer* (WH/Output). Om deze locaties te hernoemen, ga je naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad app --> Configuratie --> Locaties`, klik je op de "
":guilabel:`Locatie` om te wijzigen en werk je de naam bij."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:42
msgid "Deliver in three steps (pick + pack + ship)"
msgstr "Lever in drie stappen (pick + pack + ship)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:45
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:35
msgid "Create a sales order"
msgstr "Maak een verkooporder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:47
msgid ""
"To create a new quote, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Create`, which "
"reveals a blank quotation form. On the blank quotation form, select "
"a :guilabel:`Customer`, add a storable :guilabel:`Product`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Maak een nieuwe offerte aan via :menuselection:`Verkoop app --> Aanmaken`, "
"waarmee een leeg offerteformulier verschijnt. Selecteer op het lege "
"offerteformulier een :guilabel:`Klant`, voeg een voorraadproduct "
":guilabel:`Product` toe en klik op :guilabel:`Bevestigen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:51
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button appears in the top right of the "
"quotation form. Clicking it opens the picking order to move the ordered "
"product from `WH/Stock` to `WH/Packing Zone`."
msgstr ""
"Een slimme knop :guilabel:`Levering` verschijnt rechtsboven in het "
"offerteformulier. Klik hierop om de pickingorder te openen waarmee het "
"bestelde product van `WH/Stock` naar `WH/Packing Zone` wordt verplaatst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid ""
"After confirming the sales order, the Delivery smart button appears showing "
"three items\n"
"associated with it."
msgstr ""
"Na het bevestigen van de verkooporder verschijnt de slimme knop Levering met "
"drie items die eraan gekoppeld zijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:60
msgid "Process a picking"
msgstr "Een picking verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:62
msgid ""
"The picking order will be created once the sales order is confirmed. To view "
"the picking, navigate to the :menuselection:`Inventory app`, and locate "
"the :guilabel:`Pick` task card on the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"De pickingorder wordt aangemaakt zodra de verkooporder is bevestigd. Bekijk "
"de picking via :menuselection:`Voorraad app` en zoek de taakkaart "
":guilabel:`Pick` op het :guilabel:`Voorraadoverzicht` dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:66
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button, which reveals the picking order "
"generated from the previously confirmed sales order."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`# Te verwerken`, waarmee de pickingorder "
"verschijnt die is gegenereerd uit de eerder bevestigde verkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:69
msgid ""
"Click on the picking to process. If the product is in stock, Odoo will "
"automatically reserve the product. Click :guilabel:`Validate` to mark the "
"picking as done, and complete the transfer to the :guilabel:`Packing Zone`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de te verwerken picking. Als het product op voorraad is, reserveert "
"Odoo het product automatisch. Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de picking "
"als voltooid te markeren en de transfer naar de :guilabel:`Verpakkingszone` "
"te voltooien."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid ""
"Picking order operation showing source location and destination location."
msgstr "Pickingorder bewerking met bronlocatie en bestemmingslocatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:78
msgid "Process a packing"
msgstr "Een verpakking verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:80
msgid ""
"After validating the picking, the packing order is ready to process. Click "
"back to the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview`, and locate the :guilabel:`Pack` "
"task card on the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Na het valideren van de picking is de verpakkingsorder klaar om te "
"verwerken. Ga terug naar het :guilabel:`Voorraadoverzicht` en zoek de "
"taakkaart :guilabel:`Pack` op het dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:83
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button (in this case, :guilabel:`1 To "
"Process`). This reveals the packing order generated from the previously "
"confirmed sales order."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`# Te verwerken` (in dit geval :guilabel:`1 Te "
"verwerken`). Dit toont de verpakkingsorder die is gegenereerd uit de eerder "
"bevestigde verkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:86
msgid ""
"Click on the packing order associated with the sales order, then click "
"on :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the packing."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de verpakkingsorder die bij de verkooporder hoort en klik vervolgens "
"op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de verpakking te voltooien."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid ""
"Packing order operation showing source location and destination location."
msgstr "Verpakkingsorder bewerking met bronlocatie en bestemmingslocatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once the packing order is validated, the product leaves the :guilabel:`WH/"
"Packing Zone` location and moves to the :guilabel:`WH/Output` location. "
"Then, the status of the document will change to :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de verpakkingsorder is gevalideerd, verlaat het product de locatie "
":guilabel:`WH/Packing Zone` en verplaatst het naar de locatie :guilabel:`WH/"
"Output`. Vervolgens verandert de status van het document naar "
":guilabel:`Voltooid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:98
msgid "Process a delivery"
msgstr "Een levering verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:100
msgid ""
"Once the packing order has been validated, the delivery order is ready to "
"process. Navigate back to the original sales order to process the delivery "
"by going to :menuselection:`Sales app`, and selecting the sales order "
"created previously."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de verpakkingsorder is gevalideerd, is de leveringsorder klaar om te "
"verwerken. Ga terug naar de oorspronkelijke verkooporder om de levering te "
"verwerken via :menuselection:`Verkoop app` en selecteer de eerder "
"aangemaakte verkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:105
msgid ""
"Delivery orders can *also* be accessed by going to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Operations --> Deliveries`."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsorders zijn *ook* toegankelijk via :menuselection:`Voorraad app --> "
"Bewerkingen --> Leveringen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:108
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button now indicates there are 3 transfers, "
"instead of one. Clicking the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button shows the "
"three operations for this sales order: the picking, the packing, and the "
"delivery."
msgstr ""
"De slimme knop :guilabel:`Levering` geeft nu aan dat er 3 overboekingen zijn "
"in plaats van één. Klik op de slimme knop :guilabel:`Levering` om de drie "
"activiteiten voor deze verkooporder te zien: de picking, de verpakking en de "
"levering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:112
msgid ""
"Click the delivery (WH/OUT) transfer to open the delivery order. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de levering (WH/OUT) transfer om de leveringsorder te openen. Klik "
"vervolgens op :guilabel:`Valideren`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click Validate on the delivery order to transfer the product from the output "
"location to\n"
"the customer location."
msgstr ""
"Klik op Valideren in de leveringsorder om het product van de outputlocatie "
"naar de klantlocatie over te boeken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps.rst:119
msgid ""
"Once the delivery order is validated, the product leaves the :guilabel:`WH/"
"Output` location and moves to the :guilabel:`Partners/Customers` location. "
"Then, the status of the document will change to :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de leveringsorder is gevalideerd, verlaat het product de locatie "
":guilabel:`WH/Output` en verhuist naar de locatie :guilabel:`Partners/"
"Customers`. De status van het document verandert vervolgens in "
":guilabel:`Voltooid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:7
msgid ""
"Dropshipping is an order fulfillment strategy that allows sellers to have "
"items shipped directly from suppliers to customers. Normally, a seller "
"purchases a product from a supplier, stores it in their inventory, and ships "
"it to the end customer once an order is placed. With dropshipping, the "
"supplier is responsible for storing and shipping the item. This benefits the "
"seller by reducing inventory costs, including the price of operating "
"warehouses."
msgstr ""
"Dropshipping is een orderverwerkingsstrategie waarmee verkopers artikelen "
"rechtstreeks van leveranciers naar klanten kunnen laten verzenden. Normaal "
"gesproken koopt een verkoper een product bij een leverancier, slaat het op "
"in de voorraad en verzendt het naar de eindklant zodra een bestelling is "
"geplaatst. Bij dropshipping is de leverancier verantwoordelijk voor het "
"opslaan en verzenden van het artikel. Dit komt de verkoper ten goede door "
"voorraadkosten te verlagen, inclusief de kosten voor het exploiteren van "
"magazijnen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:14
msgid "Configure products to be dropshipped"
msgstr "Producten configureren voor dropshipping"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:16
msgid ""
"To use dropshipping as a fulfillment strategy, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Purchase` app and select :menuselection:`Configuration --"
"> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Logistics` heading, click "
"the :guilabel:`Dropshipping` checkbox, and :guilabel:`Save` to finish."
msgstr ""
"Om dropshipping als verwerkingsstrategie te gebruiken, navigeer je naar de "
"app :menuselection:`Inkoop` en selecteer je :menuselection:`Configuratie --> "
"Instellingen`. Klik onder de kop :guilabel:`Logistiek` op het selectievakje "
":guilabel:`Dropshipping` en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan` om af te ronden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:20
msgid ""
"Next, go to the :menuselection:`Sales` app, click :menuselection:`Products --"
"> Products` and choose an existing product or select :guilabel:`Create` to "
"configure a new one. On the :guilabel:`Product` page, make sure that "
"the :guilabel:`Can be Sold` and :guilabel:`Can be Purchased` checkboxes are "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ga vervolgens naar de app :menuselection:`Verkoop`, klik op "
":menuselection:`Producten --> Producten` en kies een bestaand product of "
"selecteer :guilabel:`Aanmaken` om een nieuw product te configureren. "
"Controleer op de pagina :guilabel:`Product` of de selectievakjes "
":guilabel:`Kan worden verkocht` en :guilabel:`Kan worden gekocht` zijn "
"ingeschakeld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid ""
"Enable the \"Can be Sold\" and \"Can be Purchased\" checkboxes on the "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Schakel de selectievakjes \"Kan worden verkocht\" en \"Kan worden gekocht\" "
"in op het productformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click on the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab and specify a vendor and the price "
"that they sell the product for. Multiple vendors can be added, but the "
"vendor at the top of the list will be the one automatically selected for "
"purchase orders."
msgstr ""
"Klik op het tabblad :guilabel:`Inkoop` en geef een leverancier en de prijs "
"waarvoor deze het product verkoopt op. Er kunnen meerdere leveranciers "
"worden toegevoegd, maar de leverancier bovenaan de lijst wordt automatisch "
"geselecteerd voor inkooporders."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid "The product form with a vendor specified."
msgstr "Het productformulier met een opgegeven leverancier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:37
msgid ""
"Finally, select the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Dropship` checkbox in the :guilabel:`Routes` section."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer ten slotte het tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad` en schakel het "
"selectievakje :guilabel:`Dropship` in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Routes` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid "Enable the Dropship option in the product inventory tab."
msgstr "Schakel de Dropship-optie in het voorraadtabblad van het product in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:45
msgid ""
"While it is not necessary to enable the :guilabel:`Buy` route in addition to "
"the :guilabel:`Dropship` route, enabling both provides the option of "
"dropshipping the product or purchasing it directly."
msgstr ""
"Hoewel het niet nodig is om naast de route :guilabel:`Dropship` ook de route "
":guilabel:`Kopen` in te schakelen, biedt het inschakelen van beide de "
"mogelijkheid om het product te dropshippen of direct in te kopen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:50
msgid "Fulfill orders using dropshipping"
msgstr "Orders verwerken met dropshipping"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:52
msgid ""
"When a sales order is created for a dropshipped product, an associated "
"request for quotation (RfQ) is automatically generated to purchase the "
"product from the vendor. Sales orders can be viewed in "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app by selecting :menuselection:`Orders --> "
"Orders`. Click the :guilabel:`Purchase` smart button at the top right of a "
"sales order to view the associated :abbr:`RFQ (Request for Quotation)`."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer een verkooporder wordt aangemaakt voor een dropshipped product, "
"wordt automatisch een bijbehorende offerteaanvraag gegenereerd om het "
"product bij de leverancier aan te schaffen. Verkooporders kunnen worden "
"bekeken in de app :menuselection:`Verkoop` door :menuselection:`Orders --> "
"Orders` te selecteren. Klik op de smartknop :guilabel:`Inkoop` rechtsboven "
"in een verkooporder om de bijbehorende :abbr:`Offerteaanvraag (Request for "
"Quotation)` te bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid ""
"A dropship sales order with the Purchase smart button in the top right "
"corner."
msgstr "Een dropship-verkooporder met de smartknop Inkoop rechtsboven."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:62
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`RFQ (Request for Quotation)` is confirmed, it becomes a "
"purchase order, and a dropship receipt is created and linked to it. The "
"receipt can be viewed by clicking the :guilabel:`Dropship` smart button in "
"the top-right corner of the purchase order form."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de :abbr:`Offerteaanvraag (Request for Quotation)` is bevestigd, wordt "
"het een inkooporder en wordt er een dropship-ontvangst aangemaakt en "
"gekoppeld. De ontvangst kan worden bekeken door rechtsboven op het "
"inkooporderformulier op de smartknop :guilabel:`Dropship` te klikken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid ""
"A dropship purchase order with the Receipt smart button in the top right "
"corner."
msgstr "Een dropship-inkooporder met de smartknop Ontvangst rechtsboven."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:70
msgid ""
"The dropship receipt displays :guilabel:`Partners/Vendors` in "
"the :guilabel:`Source Location` field, and :guilabel:`Partners/Customers` in "
"the :guilabel:`Destination Location` field. Upon delivery of the product to "
"the customer, click on the :guilabel:`Validate` button at the top-left of "
"the dropship receipt to confirm the delivered quantity."
msgstr ""
"De dropship-ontvangst toont :guilabel:`Partners/Leveranciers` in het veld "
":guilabel:`Bronlocatie` en :guilabel:`Partners/Klanten` in het veld "
":guilabel:`Bestemmingslocatie`. Klik na levering van het product aan de "
"klant linksboven op de dropship-ontvangst op de knop :guilabel:`Valideren` "
"om de geleverde hoeveelheid te bevestigen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid "Validate the dropship receipt after delivery."
msgstr "Valideer de dropship-ontvangst na levering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:79
msgid ""
"To view all dropship orders, simply navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory` :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard and click the "
"teal :guilabel:`# TO PROCESS` button on the :guilabel:`Dropship` card."
msgstr ""
"Om alle dropship-orders te bekijken, navigeer je naar het dashboard "
":menuselection:`Voorraad` :guilabel:`Overzicht` en klik je op de groene knop "
":guilabel:`# TE VERWERKEN` op de kaart :guilabel:`Dropship`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the green button on the Dropship card to view all dropship orders."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de groene knop op de Dropship-kaart om alle dropship-orders te "
"bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:3
msgid "Consignment: buy and sell stock without owning it"
msgstr "Consignatie: koop en verkoop voorraad zonder eigenaar te zijn"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:5
msgid ""
"Most of the time, products stored in a company's warehouse are either "
"purchased from suppliers, or are manufactured in-house. However, suppliers "
"will sometimes let companies store and sell products in the company's "
"warehouse, without having to buy those items up-front. This is called "
"*consignment*."
msgstr ""
"Meestal zijn producten die zijn opgeslagen in het magazijn van een bedrijf "
"ofwel gekocht bij leveranciers, ofwel intern geproduceerd. Soms laten "
"leveranciers bedrijven echter producten opslaan en verkopen in het magazijn "
"van het bedrijf, zonder dat deze artikelen vooraf hoeven te worden gekocht. "
"Dit wordt *consignatie* genoemd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:10
msgid ""
"Consignment is a useful method for suppliers to launch new products, and "
"easily deliver to their customers. It's also a great way for the company "
"storing the products (the consignee) to earn something back for their "
"efforts. Consignees can even charge a fee for the convenience of storing "
"products they don't actually own."
msgstr ""
"Consignatie is een handige methode voor leveranciers om nieuwe producten te "
"lanceren en deze gemakkelijk bij hun klanten af te leveren. Het is ook een "
"geweldige manier voor het bedrijf dat de producten opslaat (de "
"consignatienemer) om iets terug te verdienen voor hun inspanningen. "
"Consignatienemers kunnen zelfs kosten in rekening brengen voor het gemak van "
"het opslaan van producten die ze niet daadwerkelijk bezitten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:16
msgid "Enable the consignment setting"
msgstr "Schakel de consignatieinstelling in"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:18
msgid ""
"To receive, store, and sell consignment stock, the feature needs to be "
"enabled in the settings. To do this, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and under the :guilabel:`Traceability` section, "
"check the box next to :guilabel:`Consignment`, and then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to finish."
msgstr ""
"Om consignatievoorraad te ontvangen, op te slaan en te verkopen, moet de "
"functie worden ingeschakeld in de instellingen. Ga hiervoor naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`, en vink onder "
"het gedeelte :guilabel:`Traceerbaarheid` het vakje aan naast "
":guilabel:`Consignatie`, en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Opslaan` om te "
"voltooien."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:None
msgid "Enabled Consignment setting in Inventory configuration."
msgstr "Ingeschakelde consignatieinstelling in Voorraadinstellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:28
msgid "Receive (and store) consignment stock"
msgstr "Ontvang (en bewaar) consignatievoorraad"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:30
msgid ""
"With the feature enabled in Odoo, consignment stock can now be received into "
"a warehouse. From the main :menuselection:`Inventory` dashboard, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Receipts` section. Then, click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Met de functie ingeschakeld in Odoo kan consignatievoorraad nu in een "
"magazijn worden ontvangen. Klik vanaf het hoofddashboard van "
":menuselection:`Voorraad` naar het gedeelte :guilabel:`Ontvangsten`. Klik "
"vervolgens op :guilabel:`Aanmaken`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:35
msgid ""
"Consignment stock is not actually purchased from the vendor; it is simply "
"received and stored. Because of this, there are no quotations or purchase "
"orders involved in receiving consignment stock. So, *every* receipt of "
"consignment stock will start by creating manual receipts."
msgstr ""
"Consignatievoorraad wordt niet daadwerkelijk gekocht bij de leverancier; het "
"wordt alleen ontvangen en opgeslagen. Hierdoor zijn er geen offertes of "
"inkooporders betrokken bij het ontvangen van consignatievoorraad. Daarom "
"begint *elke* ontvangst van consignatievoorraad met het aanmaken van "
"handmatige ontvangsten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:39
msgid ""
"Choose a vendor to enter in the :guilabel:`Receive From` field, and then "
"choose the same vendor to enter in the :guilabel:`Assign Owner` field."
msgstr ""
"Kies een leverancier om in te voeren in het veld :guilabel:`Ontvangen van`, "
"en kies vervolgens dezelfde leverancier om in te voeren in het veld "
":guilabel:`Eigenaar toewijzen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:43
msgid ""
"Since the products received from the vendor will be owned by the same "
"vendor, the :guilabel:`Receive From` and :guilabel:`Assign Owner` fields "
"must match."
msgstr ""
"Omdat de producten die van de leverancier worden ontvangen eigendom zijn van "
"dezelfde leverancier, moeten de velden :guilabel:`Ontvangen van` en "
":guilabel:`Eigenaar toewijzen` overeenkomen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the vendor-related fields are set, enter products into "
"the :guilabel:`Product` lines, and set the quantities to be received into "
"the warehouse under the :guilabel:`Done` column. If the :guilabel:`Units of "
"Measure` feature is enabled, the :abbr:`UoM (Units of Measure)` can be "
"changed, as well. Once all the consignment stock has been "
"received, :guilabel:`Validate` the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de leveranciersgerelateerde velden zijn ingesteld, voer je producten "
"in op de :guilabel:`Product`regels en stel je de hoeveelheden in die in het "
"magazijn moeten worden ontvangen onder de kolom :guilabel:`Voltooid`. Als de "
"functie :guilabel:`Maateenheden` is ingeschakeld, kan de :abbr:`maateenheid "
"(maateenheden)` ook worden gewijzigd. Zodra alle consignatievoorraad is "
"ontvangen, :guilabel:`Valideer` je de ontvangst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:None
msgid "Matching vendor fields in consignment Receipt creation."
msgstr ""
"Overeenkomende leveranciersvelden bij het aanmaken van een "
"consignatieontvangst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:56
msgid "Sell and deliver consignment stock"
msgstr "Verkoop en lever consignatievoorraad"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:58
msgid ""
"Once consignment stock has been received into the warehouse, it can be sold "
"the same as any other in-stock product that has the :guilabel:`Can Be Sold` "
"option enabled on the product form."
msgstr ""
"Zodra consignatievoorraad in het magazijn is ontvangen, kan het op dezelfde "
"manier worden verkocht als elk ander product op voorraad waarvoor de optie "
":guilabel:`Kan worden verkocht` is ingeschakeld op het productformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:61
msgid ""
"To create a sales order, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales` app, and "
"from the :guilabel:`Quotations` overview, click :guilabel:`Create`. Next, "
"choose a customer to enter into the :guilabel:`Customer` field."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer om een verkooporder aan te maken naar de app "
":menuselection:`Verkoop`, en klik vanaf het overzicht :guilabel:`Offertes` "
"op :guilabel:`Aanmaken`. Kies vervolgens een klant om in te voeren in het "
"veld :guilabel:`Klant`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:66
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer` *must* be different from the :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"that supplied the consignment stock received (and stored) in the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`Klant` *moet* verschillen van de :guilabel:`Leverancier` die "
"de consignatievoorraad heeft geleverd die in het magazijn is ontvangen (en "
"opgeslagen)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:69
msgid ""
"Add the consignment product under the :guilabel:`Product` column in the "
"order lines, set the :guilabel:`Quantity`, and fill out any other pertinent "
"product details on the form. Once the quotation is complete, "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Voeg het consignatieproduct toe onder de kolom :guilabel:`Product` in de "
"orderregels, stel de :guilabel:`Hoeveelheid` in en vul eventuele andere "
"relevante productgegevens in op het formulier. Zodra de offerte compleet is, "
"klik je op :guilabel:`Bevestigen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:None
msgid "Sales order of consignment stock."
msgstr "Verkooporder van consignatievoorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:77
msgid ""
"Once the quotation has been confirmed, it becomes a sales order. From here, "
"the products can be delivered by clicking on the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart "
"button, and selecting :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de offerte is bevestigd, wordt het een verkooporder. Vanaf hier kunnen "
"de producten worden geleverd door te klikken op de knop :guilabel:`Levering` "
"en :guilabel:`Valideren` te selecteren om de levering te valideren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:82
msgid "Traceability and reporting of consignment stock"
msgstr "Traceerbaarheid en rapportage van consignatievoorraad"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:84
msgid ""
"Although consignment stock is owned by the vendor who supplied it, and not "
"by the company storing it in their warehouse, consignment products will "
"*still* appear in certain inventory reports."
msgstr ""
"Hoewel consignatievoorraad eigendom is van de leverancier die deze heeft "
"geleverd, en niet van het bedrijf dat deze in het magazijn bewaart, "
"verschijnen consignatieproducten *wel* in bepaalde voorraadrapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:87
msgid ""
"To find inventory reports, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Reporting`, "
"and choose a report to view."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad --> Rapportage` om voorraadrapportages te "
"vinden en kies een rapport om te bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:91
msgid ""
"Since the consignee does not actually own consignment stock, these products "
"are *not* reflected in the :guilabel:`Stock Valuation` report, and have no "
"impact on the consignee's inventory valuation."
msgstr ""
"Aangezien de ontvanger geen eigenaar is van consignatievoorraad, worden deze "
"producten *niet* weergegeven in het :guilabel:`Voorraadwaardering`-rapport "
"en hebben ze geen impact op de voorraadwaardering van de ontvanger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:96
msgid "Product moves report"
msgstr "Rapport productverplaatsingen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:98
msgid ""
"To view all information about on-hand stock moves, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Product Moves` dashboard by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Reporting --> Product Moves`. For "
"consignment products, the information in this report is the same as any "
"other product: the history of its product moves can be reviewed; "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity Done` and :guilabel:`Reference` document are "
"available; and its :guilabel:`Locations` are available, as well. The "
"consignment stock will originate from :guilabel:`Partner Location/Vendors`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar het :guilabel:`Productverplaatsingen`-dashboard via "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Rapportage --> Productverplaatsingen` om alle "
"informatie over aanwezige voorraadverplaatsingen te bekijken. Voor "
"consignatieproducten is de informatie in dit rapport hetzelfde als voor elk "
"ander product: de geschiedenis van de productverplaatsingen kan worden "
"bekeken; de :guilabel:`Voltooide Hoeveelheid` en het :guilabel:`Referentie`-"
"document zijn beschikbaar; en de :guilabel:`Locaties` zijn ook beschikbaar. "
"De consignatievoorraad is afkomstig van :guilabel:`Partnerlocatie/"
"Leveranciers`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:106
msgid ""
"To view a consignment product's moves by ownership, select "
"the :guilabel:`Group By` filter, choose the :guilabel:`Add Custom Group` "
"parameter, and then select :guilabel:`From Owner`, and :guilabel:`Apply` to "
"finish."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer het :guilabel:`Groepeer op`-filter om de verplaatsingen van een "
"consignatieproduct per eigenaar te bekijken, kies de parameter "
":guilabel:`Aangepaste groepering toevoegen`, selecteer vervolgens "
":guilabel:`Van eigenaar` en klik op :guilabel:`Toepassen` om af te ronden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:None
msgid "Consignment stock moves history."
msgstr "Geschiedenis van consignatievoorraadverplaatsingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:115
msgid ""
"To see forecasted units of consignment stock, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Reporting --> Forecasted Inventory`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad --> Rapportage --> Voorspelde voorraad` om "
"voorspelde eenheden consignatievoorraad te bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:119
msgid "Stock on hand report"
msgstr "Rapport aanwezige voorraad"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock.rst:121
msgid ""
"View the :guilabel:`Stock On Hand` dashboard by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Reporting --> Inventory Report`. From this "
"report, the :guilabel:`Locations` of all stock on-hand are displayed, in "
"addition to the quantities per location. For consignment products, "
"the :guilabel:`Owner` column will be populated with the owner of those "
"products, or the original vendor who supplied the products in the first "
"place."
msgstr ""
"Bekijk het :guilabel:`Aanwezige voorraad`-dashboard door te navigeren naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Rapportage --> Voorraadrapport`. Vanuit dit "
"rapport worden de :guilabel:`Locaties` van alle aanwezige voorraad "
"weergegeven, samen met de hoeveelheden per locatie. Voor "
"consignatieproducten wordt de kolom :guilabel:`Eigenaar` ingevuld met de "
"eigenaar van die producten, oftewel de oorspronkelijke leverancier die de "
"producten heeft geleverd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:5
msgid ""
"Putaway is the process of routing products to appropriate storage locations "
"upon shipment arrival."
msgstr ""
"Wegzetten is het proces waarbij producten bij aankomst van een zending naar "
"geschikte opslaglocaties worden geleid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo can accomplish this seamlessly using *putaway rules*, which dictate how "
"products move through specified warehouse locations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kan dit naadloos uitvoeren met behulp van *wegzetregels*, die bepalen "
"hoe producten zich door opgegeven magazijnlocaties verplaatsen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:10
msgid ""
"Upon shipment arrival, operations are generated based on putaway rules to "
"efficiently move products to specified locations, and ensure easy retrieval "
"for future delivery orders."
msgstr ""
"Bij aankomst van een zending worden activiteiten gegenereerd op basis van "
"wegzetregels om producten efficiënt naar opgegeven locaties te verplaatsen "
"en gemakkelijk ophalen voor toekomstige leveringsorders te waarborgen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:13
msgid ""
"In warehouses that process specific kinds of products, putaway rules can "
"also prevent volatile substances from being stored in close proximity, by "
"directing them to different locations determined by the warehouse manager."
msgstr ""
"In magazijnen die specifieke soorten producten verwerken, kunnen "
"wegzetregels ook voorkomen dat vluchtige stoffen te dicht bij elkaar worden "
"opgeslagen door ze naar verschillende locaties te leiden die door de "
"magazijnbeheerder zijn bepaald."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:18
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Putaway Rules <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=nCQMf6sj_w8>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-tutorials: wegzetregels <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nCQMf6sj_w8>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:23
msgid ""
"To use putaway rules, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and activate the :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` "
"feature under the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section. By doing so, "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` feature is also automatically activated."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Instellingen` om "
"wegzetregels te gebruiken en activeer de functie "
":guilabel:`Meerstappenroutes` onder de sectie :guilabel:`Magazijn`. Hierdoor "
"wordt ook automatisch de functie :guilabel:`Opslaglocaties` geactiveerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:27
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Klik ten slotte op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:None
msgid "Activate Multi-Step Routes in Inventory configuration settings."
msgstr ""
"Activeer meerstappenroutes in de configuratie-instellingen van Voorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:35
msgid "Define putaway rule"
msgstr "Wegzetregel definiëren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:37
msgid ""
"To manage where specific products are routed for storage, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Putaway Rules`. Use "
"the :guilabel:`New` button to configure a new putaway rule on "
"a :guilabel:`Product` or :guilabel:`Product Category` that the rule affects."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Wegzetregels` om te beheren waar specifieke producten voor opslag worden "
"gerouteerd. Gebruik de knop :guilabel:`Nieuw` om een nieuwe wegzetregel te "
"configureren op een :guilabel:`Product` of :guilabel:`Productcategorie` "
"waarop de regel van toepassing is."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:42
msgid ""
"Putaway rules can be defined either per product/product category, and/or "
"package type (the *Packages* setting must be enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings` for that). "
"Additionally, a :doc:`storage category <storage_category>` can be defined to "
"limit capacities of a storage location and route products accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Wegzetregels kunnen worden gedefinieerd per product/productcategorie en/of "
"pakkettype (de instelling *Pakketten* moet zijn ingeschakeld in "
":menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`). Daarnaast "
"kan een :doc:`opslagcategorie <storage_category>` worden gedefinieerd om de "
"capaciteit van een opslaglocatie te beperken en producten dienovereenkomstig "
"te routeren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:47
msgid ""
"In the same line, the :guilabel:`When product arrives in` location is where "
"the putaway rule is triggered to create an operation to move the product to "
"the :guilabel:`Store to` location."
msgstr ""
"Op dezelfde regel is de locatie :guilabel:`When product arrives in` waar de "
"wegzetregel wordt geactiveerd om een bewerking aan te maken om het product "
"te verplaatsen naar de locatie :guilabel:`Store to`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:50
msgid ""
"For this to work, the :guilabel:`Store to` location must be a *sub-location* "
"of the first (e.g., `WH/Stock/Fruits` is a specific, named location inside "
"`WH/Stock` to make the products stored here easier to find)."
msgstr ""
"Om dit te laten werken moet de locatie :guilabel:`Store to` een *sublocatie* "
"zijn van de eerste (bv. `WH/Stock/Fruits` is een specifieke, benoemde "
"locatie binnen `WH/Stock` om de hier opgeslagen producten gemakkelijker te "
"vinden)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:55
msgid ""
"In a warehouse location, **WH/Stock**, there are the following sub-locations:"
msgstr "In een magazijnlocatie, **WH/Stock**, zijn de volgende sublocaties:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:57
msgid "WH/Stock/Fruits"
msgstr "WH/Stock/Fruits"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:58
msgid "WH/Stock/Vegetables"
msgstr "WH/Stock/Vegetables"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:60
msgid ""
"Ensure all apples are stored in the fruits section by filling the "
"field :guilabel:`Store to` with the location `WH/Stock/Fruits` when "
"the :guilabel:`Product`, `Apple` arrives in `WH/Stock`."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat alle appels in de fruitsectie worden opgeslagen door het "
"veld :guilabel:`Store to` in te vullen met de locatie `WH/Stock/Fruits` "
"wanneer het :guilabel:`Product`, `Apple` aankomt in `WH/Stock`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:63
msgid "Repeat this for all products and hit :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Herhaal dit voor alle producten en klik op :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:0
msgid "Create putaway rules for apples and carrots."
msgstr "Maak wegzetregels aan voor appels en wortels."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:68
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Sublocation` field to specify whether to use a "
"sublocation or specify a storage category:"
msgstr ""
"Gebruik het veld :guilabel:`Sublocatie` om op te geven of een sublocatie "
"moet worden gebruikt of een opslagcategorie moet worden opgegeven:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No`: no sublocation is used. Products are directed to whatever is "
"specified in the :guilabel:`Store to` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nee`: er wordt geen sublocatie gebruikt. Producten worden geleid "
"naar wat is opgegeven in het veld :guilabel:`Opslaan in`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Last Used`: the last location that had a move associated with it "
"for that product or product category is used. If there is no last location "
"used, the destination is whatever is specified in the :guilabel:`Store to` "
"field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Laatst gebruikt`: de laatste locatie die een verplaatsing had die "
"ermee was geassocieerd voor dat product of die productcategorie wordt "
"gebruikt. Als er geen laatst gebruikte locatie is, is de bestemming wat is "
"opgegeven in het veld :guilabel:`Opslaan in`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closest Location`: the locations specified as part of a storage "
"category are used. A storage category is mandatory in the :guilabel:`Having "
"Category` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dichtstbijzijnde locatie`: de locaties die zijn opgegeven als "
"onderdeel van een opslagcategorie worden gebruikt. Een opslagcategorie is "
"verplicht in het veld :guilabel:`Met categorie`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:79
msgid ""
"To apply a putaway rule to *all* products, create an empty putaway rule with "
"no specified :guilabel:`Product` or :guilabel:`Product Category`. All "
"products are stored in the location specified in the :guilabel:`Store to` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Maak een lege wegzetregel zonder opgegeven :guilabel:`Product` of "
":guilabel:`Productcategorie` om een wegzetregel toe te passen op *alle* "
"producten. Alle producten worden opgeslagen op de locatie die is opgegeven "
"in het veld :guilabel:`Opslaan in`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:84
msgid ""
"A best practice for an empty putaway rule is to specify the :guilabel:`Last "
"used` :guilabel:`Sublocation`. Specifying :guilabel:`Last used` ensures that "
"Odoo suggests the last location used to store a product."
msgstr ""
"Een best practice voor een lege opbergregel is om de :guilabel:`Laatst "
"gebruikt` :guilabel:`Sublocatie` op te geven. Door :guilabel:`Laatst "
"gebruikt` op te geven, zorgt Odoo ervoor dat de laatste locatie wordt "
"voorgesteld die is gebruikt om een product op te slaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:89
msgid "Putaway rule priority"
msgstr "Prioriteit wegzetregels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:91
msgid ""
"Odoo selects a putaway rule based on the following priority list (from "
"highest to lowest) until a match is found:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo selecteert een wegzetregel op basis van de volgende prioriteitenlijst "
"(van hoog naar laag) totdat een overeenkomst wordt gevonden:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:94
msgid "Package type and product"
msgstr "Pakkettype en product"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:95
msgid "Package type and product category"
msgstr "Pakkettype en productcategorie"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:98
msgid "Product category"
msgstr "Productcategorie"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:101
msgid "The product `Lemonade can` has the following putaway rules configured:"
msgstr ""
"Het product `Lemonade can` heeft de volgende wegzetregels geconfigureerd:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:103
msgid ""
"When receiving a `Pallet` (:guilabel:`Package Type`) of `Lemonade cans`, it "
"is redirected to `WH/Stock/Pallets/PAL1`."
msgstr ""
"Bij het ontvangen van een `Pallet` (:guilabel:`Package Type`) van `Lemonade "
"cans` wordt dit doorgestuurd naar `WH/Stock/Pallets/PAL1`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:105
msgid ""
"`Lemonade can`'s :guilabel:`Product Category` is `All/drinks`, and when "
"receiving a `Box` of any item in this product category, items are redirected "
"to `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`Product Category` van `Lemonade can` is `All/drinks`, en bij "
"het ontvangen van een `Box` van elk artikel in deze productcategorie worden "
"artikelen doorgestuurd naar `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:107
msgid "Any product on a `Pallet` is redirected to `WH/Stock/Pallets`"
msgstr "Elk product op een `Pallet` wordt doorgestuurd naar `WH/Stock/Pallets`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:108
msgid "The product `Lemonade can` is redirected to `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`"
msgstr "Het product `Lemonade can` wordt doorgestuurd naar `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:109
msgid ""
"Items in the `All/drinks` product category are redirected to `WH/Stock/Small "
"Refrigerator`."
msgstr ""
"Artikelen in de productcategorie `All/drinks` worden doorgestuurd naar `WH/"
"Stock/Small Refrigerator`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/putaway.rst:0
msgid "Some examples of putaway rules."
msgstr "Enkele voorbeelden van wegzetregels."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:3
msgid "One-step receipt and delivery"
msgstr "Ontvangst en levering in één stap"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:9
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Inventory*, both incoming and outgoing shipments are configured to "
"process in one step, by default. This means purchases will be received "
"directly into stock, and deliveries will be moved directly from stock to "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"In Odoo *Voorraad* zijn standaard zowel inkomende als uitgaande zendingen "
"geconfigureerd om in één stap te verwerken. Dit betekent dat aankopen direct "
"in de voorraad worden ontvangen en leveringen direct van de voorraad naar "
"klanten worden verplaatst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:28
msgid ""
"Incoming and outgoing shipments do **not** need to be configured with the "
"same amount of steps."
msgstr ""
"Inkomende en uitgaande zendingen hoeven **niet** met hetzelfde aantal "
"stappen te worden geconfigureerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:16
msgid ""
"For example, a warehouse's settings can be configured so products can be "
"received directly in one step, and delivered in three steps (pick + pack + "
"ship)."
msgstr ""
"Bijvoorbeeld: de instellingen van een magazijn kunnen zo worden "
"geconfigureerd dat producten direct in één stap worden ontvangen en in drie "
"stappen worden geleverd (picken + pakken + verzenden)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:22
msgid ""
"To configure one-step receipts and deliveries for a warehouse, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, and "
"select a warehouse to edit."
msgstr ""
"Configureer ontvangst en levering in één stap voor een magazijn via "
":menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Magazijnen` en selecteer "
"een magazijn om te bewerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:25
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` tab, set :guilabel:`Incoming "
"Shipments` to :guilabel:`Receive goods directly (1 step)`, and "
"set :guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments` to :guilabel:`Deliver goods directly (1 "
"step)`."
msgstr ""
"Stel onder het tabblad :guilabel:`Magazijnconfiguratie` de optie "
":guilabel:`Inkomende zendingen` in op :guilabel:`Goederen direct ontvangen "
"(1 stap)` en stel :guilabel:`Uitgaande zendingen` in op :guilabel:`Goederen "
"direct leveren (1 stap)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Incoming and outgoing shipments set to one-step on warehouse form."
msgstr ""
"Inkomende en uitgaande zendingen ingesteld op één stap in het "
"magazijnformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:34
msgid ""
"Since one-step receipt and delivery is the default for incoming and outgoing "
"shipments in Odoo, the *Multi-Step Routes* feature is *not* required."
msgstr ""
"Omdat ontvangst en levering in één stap de standaard is voor inkomende en "
"uitgaande zendingen in Odoo, is de functie *Meerstapsroutes* *niet* vereist."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:37
msgid ""
"However, for the :guilabel:`Shipments` settings to appear on a warehouse "
"form, the feature **must** be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Voor het verschijnen van de instellingen :guilabel:`Zendingen` in een "
"magazijnformulier **moet** de functie echter zijn ingeschakeld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:40
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:39
msgid ""
"To enable *Multi-Step Routes*, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section, tick "
"the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Doing so also activates the :guilabel:`Storage "
"Locations` feature."
msgstr ""
"Schakel *Meerstapsroutes* in via :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Vink onder de sectie :guilabel:`Magazijn` "
"het selectievakje naast :guilabel:`Meerstapsroutes` aan en klik op "
":guilabel:`Opslaan`. Hierdoor wordt ook de functie "
":guilabel:`Opslaglocaties` geactiveerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:48
msgid "Receive goods directly (1 step)"
msgstr "Goederen direct ontvangen (1 stap)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:50
msgid ""
"When products are received in one step, they will move from the vendor "
"location to warehouse stock in the database immediately upon validation of a "
"purchase order (PO)."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer producten in één stap worden ontvangen, verplaatsen ze in de "
"database direct van de leverancierslocatie naar de magazijnvoorraad zodra "
"een inkooporder (PO) is gevalideerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:79
msgid ""
"To create a |PO|, navigate to the :menuselection:`Purchase app`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a blank :guilabel:`Request for Quotation` "
"(RfQ) form."
msgstr ""
"Maak een |PO| via de :menuselection:`Inkoop-app` en klik op "
":guilabel:`Nieuw`. Er verschijnt een leeg formulier voor een "
":guilabel:`Offerteaanvraag` (RfQ)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:59
msgid ""
"Add a vendor in the :guilabel:`Supplier` field. Then, fill out the various "
"fields on the |RfQ|, as necessary."
msgstr ""
"Voeg een leverancier toe in het veld :guilabel:`Leverancier`. Vul vervolgens "
"de verschillende velden in de |RfQ| in zoals nodig."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Filled out new request for quotation form."
msgstr "Ingevuld nieuw formulier voor offerteaanvraag."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:66
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:89
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select a product to add to the |RfQ|."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder het tabblad :guilabel:`Producten` op :guilabel:`Product "
"toevoegen` en selecteer een product om aan de |RfQ| toe te voegen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:92
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm Order`. This moves the |RfQ| to "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase Order` stage."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Order bevestigen` zodra je klaar bent. Hierdoor wordt de "
"|RfQ| verplaatst naar de fase :guilabel:`Inkooporder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:95
msgid ""
"Once the |PO| is confirmed, a :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button appears at "
"the top of the form. Clicking the smart button opens the warehouse receipt "
"(WH/IN) form."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de |PO| is bevestigd, verschijnt bovenaan het formulier een slimme "
"knop :guilabel:`Ontvangst`. Klik op de slimme knop om het "
"magazijnontvangstformulier (WH/IN) te openen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Receipt smart button on confirmed purchase order form."
msgstr "Slimme knop voor ontvangst op bevestigd inkooporderformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/subcontracting/subcontracting_basic.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/subcontracting/subcontracting_dropship.rst:203
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/subcontracting/subcontracting_resupply.rst:159
msgid "Process receipt"
msgstr "Ontvangst verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:82
msgid ""
"From the warehouse receipt form, the products ordered can be received into "
"the warehouse. To receive the products, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Once "
"validated, the receipt moves to the :guilabel:`Done` stage."
msgstr ""
"Vanaf het magazijnontvangstformulier kunnen de bestelde producten in het "
"magazijn worden ontvangen. Ontvang de producten door op "
":guilabel:`Valideren` te klikken. Zodra de ontvangst is gevalideerd, wordt "
"deze verplaatst naar de fase :guilabel:`Voltooid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Validated warehouse receipt in Done stage."
msgstr "Gevalideerde magazijnontvangst in fase Voltooid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:90
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:121
msgid ""
"Click back to the |PO| (via the breadcrumbs, at the top of the form) to view "
"the |PO| form. On the product line, the quantity in the :guilabel:`Received` "
"column now matches the ordered :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
"Klik terug naar de |PO| (via het kruimelpad bovenaan het formulier) om het "
"|PO|formulier te bekijken. Op de productregel komt de hoeveelheid in de "
"kolom :guilabel:`Ontvangen` nu overeen met de bestelde "
":guilabel:`Hoeveelheid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:97
msgid "Deliver goods directly (1 step)"
msgstr "Goederen direct leveren (1 stap)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:99
msgid ""
"When products are delivered in one step, they will move from warehouse stock "
"to the customer location in the database immediately upon validation of a "
"sales order (SO)."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer producten in één stap worden geleverd, verplaatsen ze zich in de "
"database direct na validatie van een verkooporder (SO) van de "
"magazijnvoorraad naar de klantlocatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:156
msgid "Create sales order"
msgstr "Verkooporder aanmaken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:105
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:158
msgid ""
"To create a |SO|, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales app`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a blank sales quotation form."
msgstr ""
"Om een |SO| aan te maken, navigeer je naar de :menuselection:`Verkoop-app` "
"en klik je op :guilabel:`Nieuw`. Dit opent een leeg verkoopofferteformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:161
msgid ""
"Add a customer in the :guilabel:`Customer` field. Then, fill out the various "
"fields on the sales quotation form, as necessary."
msgstr ""
"Voeg een klant toe in het veld :guilabel:`Klant`. Vul vervolgens indien "
"nodig de verschillende velden op het verkoopofferteformulier in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Filled out new sales quotation form."
msgstr "Ingevuld nieuw verkoopofferteformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:115
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Product` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select a product to add to the sales order quotation."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder het tabblad :guilabel:`Product` op :guilabel:`Product toevoegen` "
"en selecteer een product om toe te voegen aan de verkooporderofferte."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:118
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:171
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm`. This moves the quotation to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Order` stage."
msgstr ""
"Klik zodra je klaar bent op :guilabel:`Bevestigen`. Dit verplaatst de "
"offerte naar de fase :guilabel:`Verkooporder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:174
msgid ""
"Once the |SO| is confirmed, a :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button appears at "
"the top of the form. Clicking the smart button opens the warehouse delivery "
"(WH/OUT) form."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de |SO| is bevestigd, verschijnt er bovenaan het formulier een slimme "
"knop :guilabel:`Levering`. Klik je op de slimme knop, dan opent het "
"magazijnleveringsformulier (WH/OUT)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Delivery smart button on confirmed sales order form."
msgstr "Slimme knop Levering op bevestigd verkooporderformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:207
msgid "Process delivery"
msgstr "Levering verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:131
msgid ""
"From the warehouse delivery form, the products ordered by the customer can "
"be delivered from the warehouse. To deliver the products, change the value "
"in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field to match the ordered quantity in "
"the :guilabel:`Demand` field."
msgstr ""
"Vanaf het magazijnleveringsformulier kunnen de door de klant bestelde "
"producten vanuit het magazijn worden geleverd. Om de producten te leveren, "
"wijzig je de waarde in het veld :guilabel:`Hoeveelheid` zodat deze "
"overeenkomt met de bestelde hoeveelheid in het veld :guilabel:`Vraag`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:135
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:225
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Once validated, the delivery order "
"moves to the :guilabel:`Done` stage."
msgstr ""
"Klik zodra je klaar bent op :guilabel:`Valideren`. Zodra deze is "
"gevalideerd, gaat de leveringsorder naar de fase :guilabel:`Voltooid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:None
msgid "Validated delivery order in Done stage."
msgstr "Gevalideerde leveringsorder in fase Voltooid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:142
msgid ""
"Click back to the |SO| (via the breadcrumbs, at the top of the form) to view "
"the |SO| form. On the product line, the quantity in "
"the :guilabel:`Delivered` column now matches the "
"ordered :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
"Klik terug naar de |SO| (via het kruimelpad bovenaan het formulier) om het "
"|SO|formulier te bekijken. Op de productregel komt de hoeveelheid in de "
"kolom :guilabel:`Geleverd` nu overeen met de bestelde "
":guilabel:`Hoeveelheid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_one_step.rst:147
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:229
msgid ":doc:`../daily_operations`"
msgstr ":doc:`../daily_operations`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:3
msgid "Two-step receipt and delivery"
msgstr "Ontvangst en levering in twee stappen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:10
msgid ""
"Depending on a company's needs, receiving and shipping products in and out "
"of the warehouse might require multi-step operations. In Odoo *Inventory*, "
"this can be done using *Multi-Step Routes*."
msgstr ""
"Afhankelijk van de behoeften van een bedrijf kan het ontvangen en verzenden "
"van producten van en naar het magazijn activiteiten in meerdere stappen "
"vereisen. In Odoo *Voorraad* kan dit worden gedaan met *Routes in meerdere "
"stappen*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:13
msgid ""
"In the two-step receipt process, products are received in an input area, "
"then transferred to stock. This kind of process for incoming shipments might "
"be beneficial for warehouses with specific storage locations, such as "
"freezers and refrigerators, secured locked areas, or special aisles and "
"shelves."
msgstr ""
"Bij het ontvangstproces in twee stappen worden producten ontvangen in een "
"invoergebied en vervolgens overgebracht naar de voorraad. Dit soort proces "
"voor inkomende zendingen kan nuttig zijn voor magazijnen met specifieke "
"opslaglocaties, zoals vriezers en koelkasten, beveiligde afgesloten ruimtes "
"of speciale gangpaden en schappen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:17
msgid ""
"Products can be sorted according to where they are going to be stored, and "
"employees can stock all the products going to a specific location. The "
"products are *not* available for further processing, until they are "
"transferred into stock."
msgstr ""
"Producten kunnen worden gesorteerd op basis van waar ze worden opgeslagen, "
"en werknemers kunnen alle producten op voorraad zetten die naar een "
"specifieke locatie gaan. De producten zijn *niet* beschikbaar voor verdere "
"verwerking totdat ze naar de voorraad zijn overgebracht."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the two-step delivery process, products are first picked from their "
"respective location in the warehouse, then transferred to an output location "
"before being shipped to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Bij het tweestaps leveringsproces worden producten eerst gepickt van hun "
"respectievelijke locatie in het magazijn en vervolgens overgebracht naar een "
"outputlocatie voordat ze naar de klant worden verzonden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:24
msgid ""
"This might be beneficial for companies using a First In, First Out (FIFO), "
"Last In, First Out (LIFO), or First Expired, First Out (FEFO) removal "
"strategy."
msgstr ""
"Dit kan nuttig zijn voor bedrijven die een First In, First Out (FIFO), Last "
"In, First Out (LIFO) of First Expired, First Out (FEFO) verwijderstrategie "
"gebruiken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:30
msgid ""
"For example, a warehouse's settings can be configured so products can be "
"received in two steps (input + stock), and delivered in three steps (pick + "
"pack + ship)."
msgstr ""
"Een magazijn kan bijvoorbeeld zo worden geconfigureerd dat producten in twee "
"stappen kunnen worden ontvangen (input + voorraad) en in drie stappen kunnen "
"worden geleverd (pick + pack + ship)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:36
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Inventory*, both incoming and outgoing shipments are configured to "
"process in one step, by default. To change these settings, the *Multi-Step "
"Routes* feature must be enabled."
msgstr ""
"In Odoo *Voorraad* zijn zowel inkomende als uitgaande zendingen standaard "
"geconfigureerd om in één stap te worden verwerkt. Om deze instellingen te "
"wijzigen, moet de functie *Meerstaps routes* worden ingeschakeld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Enabled Multi-Step Routes feature in Inventory app settings."
msgstr ""
"Ingeschakelde functie Meerstaps routes in de instellingen van de Voorraad-"
"app."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:48
msgid ""
"Next, configure a warehouse for two-step receipts and deliveries. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, and "
"select a warehouse to edit."
msgstr ""
"Configureer vervolgens een magazijn voor tweestaps ontvangsten en "
"leveringen. Navigeer naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Magazijnen` en selecteer een magazijn om te bewerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:51
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` tab, set :guilabel:`Incoming "
"Shipments` to :guilabel:`Receive goods in input and then stock (2 steps)`, "
"and set :guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments` to :guilabel:`Send goods in output "
"and then deliver (2 steps)`."
msgstr ""
"Stel onder het tabblad :guilabel:`Magazijnconfiguratie` de "
":guilabel:`Inkomende zendingen` in op :guilabel:`Goederen ontvangen in input "
"en vervolgens voorraad (2 stappen)` en stel :guilabel:`Uitgaande zendingen` "
"in op :guilabel:`Goederen verzenden in output en vervolgens leveren (2 "
"stappen)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Incoming and outgoing shipments set to two-step on warehouse form."
msgstr ""
"Inkomende en uitgaande zendingen ingesteld op twee stappen op het "
"magazijnformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:60
msgid ""
"Selecting two-step receipts and deliveries automatically creates new *Input* "
"and *Output* warehouse locations in the database, named `WH/Input` and `WH/"
"Output`, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Het selecteren van tweestaps ontvangsten en leveringen maakt automatisch "
"nieuwe *Input-* en *Output-*magazijnlocaties aan in de database, "
"respectievelijk genaamd `WH/Input` en `WH/Output`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:63
msgid ""
"To rename or edit these locations, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Configuration --> Locations`, and select the desired location."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Locaties` en "
"selecteer de gewenste locatie om deze locaties te hernoemen of te bewerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:66
msgid ""
"On the location's form, change the :guilabel:`Location Name`, and make any "
"other necessary changes."
msgstr ""
"Wijzig op het locatieformulier de :guilabel:`Locatienaam` en breng eventuele "
"andere noodzakelijke wijzigingen aan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:70
msgid "Process receipt in two steps (input + stock)"
msgstr "Ontvangst verwerken in twee stappen (input + voorraad)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:72
msgid ""
"When products are received in two steps, they first move from the vendor "
"location to an input location. Then, they move from the input location to "
"warehouse stock in the database, upon validation of a purchase order (PO), "
"and a subsequent internal transfer."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer producten in twee stappen worden ontvangen, verplaatsen ze zich "
"eerst van de leverancierslocatie naar een inputlocatie. Vervolgens "
"verplaatsen ze zich van de inputlocatie naar de magazijnvoorraad in de "
"database bij validatie van een inkooporder (PO) en een daaropvolgende "
"interne transfer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:82
msgid ""
"Add a vendor in the :guilabel:`Vendor` field. Then, fill out the various "
"fields on the |RfQ|, as necessary."
msgstr ""
"Voeg een leverancier toe in het veld :guilabel:`Leverancier`. Vul vervolgens "
"de verschillende velden op de |RfQ| in, indien nodig."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Filled out new Request for Quotation from vendor."
msgstr "Ingevulde nieuwe Offerteaanvraag van leverancier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Delivery smart button for validated purchase order."
msgstr "Levering-smartknop voor gevalideerde inkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:103
msgid ""
"For businesses with multiple warehouses that have different step "
"configurations, the :guilabel:`Deliver To` field on the |PO| form **must** "
"be specified as the correct *input location* connected to the two-step "
"warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Voor bedrijven met meerdere magazijnen die verschillende stapconfiguraties "
"hebben, **moet** het veld :guilabel:`Leveren aan` op het |PO|formulier "
"worden opgegeven als de juiste *inputlocatie* die is verbonden met het "
"tweestapsmagazijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:107
msgid ""
"This can be done by selecting the warehouse from the drop-down menu that "
"includes the `Receipts` label at the end of the name."
msgstr ""
"Dit kan worden gedaan door het magazijn te selecteren uit het "
"vervolgkeuzemenu dat het label `Receipts` aan het einde van de naam bevat."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:113
msgid ""
"From the warehouse receipt form, the products ordered can be received into "
"the warehouse. To receive the products, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Once "
"validated, the receipt moves to the :guilabel:`Done` stage, and the products "
"move to the :guilabel:`WH/Input` location."
msgstr ""
"Vanaf het magazijnontvangstformulier kunnen de bestelde producten in het "
"magazijn worden ontvangen. Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de producten te "
"ontvangen. Eenmaal gevalideerd, gaat de ontvangst naar de fase "
":guilabel:`Voltooid` en verplaatsen de producten zich naar de locatie "
":guilabel:`WH/Input`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Receipt form for products ordered from vendor."
msgstr "Ontvangstformulier voor producten besteld bij leverancier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:126
msgid "Process internal transfer"
msgstr "Interne overboeking verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:128
msgid ""
"Once the receipt is validated, an internal transfer is created and ready to "
"process."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de ontvangst gevalideerd is, wordt een interne overboeking aangemaakt "
"en klaar om te verwerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:130
msgid ""
"To view the internal transfer, navigate to the :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app`, and locate the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` task card."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar de :menuselection:`Voorraad-app` en zoek de :guilabel:`Interne "
"overboekingen` taakkaart om de interne overboeking te bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:133
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button on the task card to reveal a list "
"of all internal transfers to process, and select the transfer associated "
"with the previously validated receipt."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de :guilabel:`# Te verwerken` knop op de taakkaart om een lijst van "
"alle te verwerken interne overboekingen te tonen en selecteer de overboeking "
"die gekoppeld is aan de eerder gevalideerde ontvangst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:136
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the transfer, and move "
"the product from :guilabel:`WH/Input` to :guilabel:`WH/Stock`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` zodra je klaar bent om de overboeking te "
"voltooien en het product te verplaatsen van :guilabel:`WH/Input` naar "
":guilabel:`WH/Stock`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:139
msgid ""
"Once the transfer is validated, the products enter inventory, and are "
"available for customer deliveries or manufacturing orders."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de overboeking gevalideerd is, komen de producten in de voorraad en "
"zijn ze beschikbaar voor klantleveringen of productieorders."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Internal transfer form for products ordered from vendor."
msgstr "Interne overboekingsformulier voor producten besteld bij leverancier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:149
msgid "Process delivery order in two steps (pick + ship)"
msgstr "Leveringsorder verwerken in twee stappen (pick + verzending)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:151
msgid ""
"When products are delivered in two steps, they move from warehouse stock to "
"an output location. Then, they move from the output location to a customer "
"location in the database, upon validation of a picking order, and a "
"subsequent delivery order (DO)."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer producten in twee stappen geleverd worden, verplaatsen ze zich van "
"magazijnvoorraad naar een uitvoerlocatie. Vervolgens verplaatsen ze zich van "
"de uitvoerlocatie naar een klantlocatie in de database, na validatie van een "
"pickingorder en een daaropvolgende leveringsorder (DO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Filled out new sales order form."
msgstr "Ingevuld nieuw verkooporderformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:168
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select a product to add to the sales order quotation."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder het :guilabel:`Orderregels` tabblad op :guilabel:`Voeg een "
"product toe` en selecteer een product om toe te voegen aan de "
"verkooporderofferte."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Delivery smart button on validated sales order form."
msgstr "Levering smart button op gevalideerd verkooporderformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:182
msgid "Process picking"
msgstr "Picking verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:184
msgid ""
"Once the sales order is confirmed, a picking order is generated and ready to "
"process."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de verkooporder bevestigd is, wordt een pickingorder gegenereerd en "
"klaar om te verwerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:186
msgid ""
"To complete the picking, navigate to the :guilabel:`Inventory app`, and "
"locate the :guilabel:`Pick` task card on the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` "
"dashboard. Alternatively, the picking order can also be accessed via "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button at the top of the sales order form."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar de :guilabel:`Voorraad-app` om de picking te voltooien en zoek "
"de :guilabel:`Pick` taakkaart op het :guilabel:`Voorraadbeheer` dashboard. "
"Als alternatief kan de pickingorder ook benaderd worden via de "
":guilabel:`levering` smart button bovenaan het verkooporderformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:190
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` page, click the :guilabel:`# To "
"Process` button on the :guilabel:`Pick` task card. This reveals a list of "
"all pickings to process."
msgstr ""
"Klik vanaf de :guilabel:`Voorraadbeheer` pagina op de :guilabel:`# Te "
"verwerken` knop op de :guilabel:`Pick` taakkaart. Dit toont een lijst van "
"alle pickings die verwerkt moeten worden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:193
msgid ""
"Click on the picking (WH/PICK) operation associated with the sales order to "
"reveal the picking order."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de picking (WH/PICK) bewerking die gekoppeld is aan de verkooporder "
"om de pickingorder te openen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Picking order form for products included in sales order."
msgstr "Pickingorderformulier voor producten opgenomen in verkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:200
msgid ""
"Manually set the quantity by changing the value in the :guilabel:`Quantity` "
"column, to match the value in the :guilabel:`Demand` column."
msgstr ""
"Stel de hoeveelheid handmatig in door de waarde in de "
":guilabel:`Hoeveelheid` kolom te wijzigen, zodat deze overeenkomt met de "
"waarde in de :guilabel:`Vraag` kolom."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:203
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the picking, and move the "
"product from :guilabel:`WH/Stock` to :guilabel:`WH/Output.`"
msgstr ""
"Klik zodra gereed op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de picking te voltooien en het "
"product van :guilabel:`WH/Stock` naar :guilabel:`WH/Output` te verplaatsen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:209
msgid ""
"Once the picking is validated, a delivery order is created, and ready to "
"process. Clicking the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button on the sales order "
"form reveals the newly created delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de picking is gevalideerd, wordt er een leveringsorder aangemaakt die "
"klaar is om te verwerken. Klik op de slimme knop :guilabel:`Levering` op het "
"verkooporderformulier om de nieuw aangemaakte leveringsorder te tonen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:212
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to view the delivery order, navigate back to "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` page, via the breadcrumbs, and locate "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` task card."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer anders terug naar de pagina :guilabel:`Voorraadoverzicht` via de "
"breadcrumbs en zoek de taakkaart :guilabel:`Leveringsorders`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:215
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button on the task card to reveal a list "
"of all delivery orders to process, and select the order associated with the "
"previously validated picking."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`# Te verwerken` op de taakkaart om een lijst van "
"alle te verwerken leveringsorders te tonen en selecteer de order die is "
"gekoppeld aan de eerder gevalideerde picking."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:None
msgid "Delivery order form for products ordered by customer."
msgstr "Leveringsorderformulier voor door klant bestelde producten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps.rst:222
msgid ""
"To deliver the products, change the value in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field "
"to match the ordered quantity in the :guilabel:`Demand` field."
msgstr ""
"Wijzig de waarde in het veld :guilabel:`Hoeveelheid` zodat deze overeenkomt "
"met de bestelde hoeveelheid in het veld :guilabel:`Vraag` om de producten te "
"leveren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:3
msgid "Three-step receipt"
msgstr "Ontvangst in drie stappen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:5
msgid ""
"Some companies require a quality control process before receiving goods from "
"suppliers. To accomplish this, Odoo has a three-step process for receiving "
"goods."
msgstr ""
"Sommige bedrijven vereisen een kwaliteitscontroleproces voordat goederen van "
"leveranciers worden ontvangen. Om dit te realiseren heeft Odoo een proces in "
"drie stappen voor het ontvangen van goederen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:8
msgid ""
"In the three-step receipt process, products are received in an input area, "
"then transferred to a quality area for inspection. Products that pass the "
"quality inspection are then transferred into stock. The products are not "
"available for further processing until they are transferred out of the "
"quality area and into stock."
msgstr ""
"In het proces voor ontvangst in drie stappen worden producten ontvangen in "
"een invoergebied, vervolgens overgebracht naar een kwaliteitsgebied voor "
"inspectie. Producten die de kwaliteitsinspectie doorstaan, worden vervolgens "
"overgebracht naar voorraad. De producten zijn pas beschikbaar voor verdere "
"verwerking nadat ze vanuit het kwaliteitsgebied naar voorraad zijn "
"overgebracht."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:16
msgid ""
"Odoo is configured by default to :doc:`receive and deliver goods in one step "
"<receipts_delivery_one_step>`, so the settings need to be changed in order "
"to utilize three-step receipts. First, make sure the *Multi-Step Routes* "
"option is enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> "
"Settings --> Warehouse`. Note that activating :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` "
"will also activate *Storage Locations*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo is standaard geconfigureerd om :doc:`goederen in één stap te ontvangen "
"en te leveren <receipts_delivery_one_step>`, dus de instellingen moeten "
"worden gewijzigd om ontvangst in drie stappen te gebruiken. Zorg er eerst "
"voor dat de optie *Routes in meerdere stappen* is ingeschakeld in "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Instellingen --> Magazijn`. "
"Merk op dat het activeren van :guilabel:`Routes in meerdere stappen` ook "
"*Opslaglocaties* activeert."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Activate multi-step routes and storage locations in Inventory settings."
msgstr ""
"Activeer routes in meerdere stappen en opslaglocaties in Voorraad-"
"instellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:26
msgid ""
"Next, the warehouse needs to be configured for three-step receipts. To do "
"that, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, "
"and select the desired warehouse to be edited. Doing so reveals the detail "
"form for that specific warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Vervolgens moet het magazijn worden geconfigureerd voor ontvangst in drie "
"stappen. Ga hiervoor naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Magazijnen` en selecteer het gewenste magazijn om te bewerken. Dit toont het "
"detailformulier voor dat specifieke magazijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:30
msgid ""
"On that :guilabel:`Warehouse` detail form page, select :guilabel:`Receive "
"goods in input, then quality and then stock (3 steps)` "
"for :guilabel:`Incoming Shipments`."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer op die detailformulierpagina van het :guilabel:`Magazijn` de optie "
":guilabel:`Goederen ontvangen in invoer, dan kwaliteit en dan voorraad (3 "
"stappen)` voor :guilabel:`Inkomende zendingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Set incoming shipment option to receive in three steps."
msgstr "Stel de optie voor inkomende zendingen in op ontvangen in drie stappen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:37
msgid ""
"Activating three-step receipts and deliveries creates two new internal "
"locations: *Input* (WH/Input), and *Quality Control* (WH/Quality Control). "
"To rename these locations, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Locations`, then click on the desired location to change "
"(or update) the name."
msgstr ""
"Het activeren van ontvangsten en leveringen in drie stappen creëert twee "
"nieuwe interne locaties: *Invoer* (WH/Input) en *Kwaliteitscontrole* (WH/"
"Quality Control). Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Locaties` om deze locaties te hernoemen, klik vervolgens op de gewenste "
"locatie om de naam te wijzigen (of bij te werken)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:43
msgid "Receive in three steps (input + quality + stock)"
msgstr "Ontvang in drie stappen (invoer + kwaliteit + voorraad)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:46
msgid "Create a purchase order"
msgstr "Maak een inkooporder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:48
msgid ""
"To create a new :abbr:`RfQ (Request for Quotation)`, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> New`, which reveals a blank :abbr:`RfQ "
"(Request for Quotation)` form page. On this page, select "
"a :guilabel:`Vendor`, add a storable :guilabel:`Product`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm Order`."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar :menuselection:`Inkoop-app --> Nieuw` om een nieuwe "
":abbr:`Offerteaanvraag (Request for Quotation)` aan te maken. Dit toont een "
"leeg formulier voor een :abbr:`Offerteaanvraag (Request for Quotation)`. "
"Selecteer op deze pagina een :guilabel:`Leverancier`, voeg een "
"voorraadproduct :guilabel:`Product` toe en klik op :guilabel:`Order "
"bevestigen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:52
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button will appear in the top right, and the "
"receipt will be associated with the purchase order. Clicking on "
"the :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button will show the receipt order."
msgstr ""
"In de rechterbovenhoek verschijnt een slimme knop :guilabel:`Ontvangst` en "
"de ontvangst wordt gekoppeld aan de inkooporder. Klik op de slimme knop "
":guilabel:`Ontvangst` om de ontvangstorder te tonen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "After confirming a purchase order, a Receipt smart button will appear."
msgstr ""
"Na het bevestigen van een inkooporder verschijnt een slimme knop Ontvangst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:61
msgid "Process a receipt"
msgstr "Verwerk een ontvangst"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:63
msgid ""
"Once the purchase order (PO) is confirmed, a receipt (`WH/IN`) operation is "
"generated and ready to process."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de inkooporder (IO) is bevestigd, wordt een ontvangstbewerking (`WH/"
"IN`) aangemaakt en is deze klaar om te verwerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:66
msgid ""
"The receipt can be confirmed from the original purchase order form, or it "
"can be accessed by navigating to the :menuselection:`Inventory app`, and "
"locating the :guilabel:`Receipts` task card."
msgstr ""
"De ontvangst kan worden bevestigd vanuit het oorspronkelijke "
"inkooporderformulier, of deze kan worden geopend door te navigeren naar de "
":menuselection:`Voorraad-app` en de taakkaart :guilabel:`Ontvangsten` te "
"lokaliseren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:69
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button to reveal all incoming receipts to "
"process. Click the receipt associated with the previous purchase order."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`# Te verwerken` om alle inkomende ontvangsten "
"weer te geven die verwerkt moeten worden. Klik op de ontvangst die hoort bij "
"de vorige inkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:72
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the receipt, and move the product to "
"the destination location, :guilabel:`WH/Input`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de ontvangst te valideren en het product te "
"verplaatsen naar de bestemmingslocatie, :guilabel:`WH/Input`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Receipt operation for product being moved to WH/Input location."
msgstr ""
"Ontvangstbewerking voor product dat wordt verplaatst naar WH/Input-locatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:80
msgid "Process a transfer to Quality Control"
msgstr "Een transfer naar kwaliteitscontrole verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:82
msgid ""
"Once the receipt has been validated, an internal transfer operation to move "
"the product to quality control is ready to process."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de ontvangst is gevalideerd, is een interne transferbewerking om het "
"product naar kwaliteitscontrole te verplaatsen klaar om te verwerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:85
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` in the breadcrumbs to navigate back to "
"the dashboard, and locate the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` task card."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Voorraadoverzicht` in het kruimelpad om terug te "
"navigeren naar het dashboard en lokaliseer de taakkaart :guilabel:`Interne "
"verplaatsingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:88
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`# To Process` button to reveal all internal transfers "
"to process. Then, choose the internal transfer associated with the validated "
"receipt."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`# Te verwerken` om alle interne verplaatsingen "
"weer te geven die verwerkt moeten worden. Kies vervolgens de interne "
"verplaatsing die hoort bij de gevalideerde ontvangst."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:91
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the transfer, and move "
"the product from :guilabel:`WH/Input` to :guilabel:`WH/Quality Control`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de transfer te voltooien en het product te "
"verplaatsen van :guilabel:`WH/Input` naar :guilabel:`WH/Kwaliteitscontrole`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Internal transfer for product being moved to quality control zone."
msgstr ""
"Interne transfer voor product dat wordt verplaatst naar "
"kwaliteitscontrolezone."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:99
msgid "Process a transfer to stock"
msgstr "Een transfer naar voorraad verwerken"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once the internal transfer to move the product to quality control has been "
"validated, another internal transfer operation to move the product into "
"warehouse stock is ready to process."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de interne transfer om het product naar kwaliteitscontrole te "
"verplaatsen is gevalideerd, is een andere interne transferbewerking om het "
"product naar de magazijnvoorraad te verplaatsen klaar om te verwerken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:104
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`YourCompany: Internal Transfers` in the breadcrumbs to "
"reveal the list of all internal transfers to process. Then, select the new "
"internal transfer to move the product from `WH/Quality Control` to `WH/"
"Stock`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`JouwBedrijf: Interne verplaatsingen` in het kruimelpad om "
"de lijst van alle te verwerken interne verplaatsingen weer te geven. "
"Selecteer vervolgens de nieuwe interne verplaatsing om het product te "
"verplaatsen van `WH/Kwaliteitscontrole` naar `WH/Voorraad`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:108
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the transfer, and move "
"the product from :guilabel:`WH/Quality Control` to :guilabel:`WH/Stock`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de transfer te voltooien en het product te "
"verplaatsen van :guilabel:`WH/Kwaliteitscontrole` naar :guilabel:`WH/"
"Voorraad`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps.rst:None
msgid "Internal transfer for product being moved to warehouse stock."
msgstr ""
"Interne transfer voor product dat wordt verplaatst naar magazijnvoorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *storage category* is used with :doc:`putaway rules <putaway>` to assign a "
"storage location to incoming products while accounting for the capacity of "
"that location. Assigning categories to storage locations tells Odoo these "
"locations meet specific requirements, such as temperature or accessibility. "
"Odoo then evaluates these locations, based on defined capacity, and "
"recommends the best one on the warehouse transfer form."
msgstr ""
"Een *opslagcategorie* wordt gebruikt met :doc:`wegzetregels <putaway>` om "
"een opslaglocatie aan inkomende producten toe te wijzen, rekening houdend "
"met de capaciteit van die locatie. Het toewijzen van categorieën aan "
"opslaglocaties vertelt Odoo dat deze locaties aan specifieke vereisten "
"voldoen, zoals temperatuur of toegankelijkheid. Odoo evalueert vervolgens "
"deze locaties op basis van gedefinieerde capaciteit en beveelt de beste aan "
"op het magazijntransferformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:11
msgid "Follow these steps to complete the setup:"
msgstr "Volg deze stappen om de installatie te voltooien:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable features in the settings <inventory/routes/enable-storage-"
"categories>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Schakel functies in via de instellingen <inventory/routes/enable-"
"storage-categories>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Define capacity limitations <inventory/routes/define-storage>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Definieer capaciteitsbeperkingen <inventory/routes/define-storage>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:15
msgid ""
"Assign a :ref:`category to storage locations <inventory/routes/assign-"
"location>`"
msgstr ""
"Wijs een :ref:`categorie toe aan opslaglocaties <inventory/routes/assign-"
"location>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:16
msgid ""
"Add the storage category as an attribute to a :ref:`putaway rule <inventory/"
"routes/set-putaway-attribute>`"
msgstr ""
"Voeg de opslagcategorie toe als een kenmerk aan een :ref:`wegzetregel "
"<inventory/routes/set-putaway-attribute>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:20
msgid ":doc:`putaway`"
msgstr ":doc:`putaway`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:25
msgid "Enable storage categories"
msgstr "Schakel opslagcategorieën in"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:27
msgid ""
"To enable storage categories, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Then, in the *Warehouse* section, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` features "
"are enabled."
msgstr ""
"Om opslagcategorieën in te schakelen, ga je naar :menuselection:`Voorraad "
"app --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Zorg er vervolgens in de sectie "
"*Magazijn* voor dat de functies :guilabel:`Opslaglocaties` en "
":guilabel:`Meerstapsroutes` zijn ingeschakeld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:31
msgid ""
"To set capacities by :ref:`package type <inventory/routes/set-capacity-"
"package>`, also make sure :guilabel:`Packages` is enabled in the "
"*Operations* section. Click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Om capaciteiten per :ref:`pakkettype <inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>"
"` in te stellen, zorg je er ook voor dat :guilabel:`Pakketten` is "
"ingeschakeld in de sectie *Bewerkingen*. Klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:None
msgid ""
"Enable Storage Locations and Multi-Step Routes to enable storage categories."
msgstr ""
"Schakel Opslaglocaties en Meerstapsroutes in om opslagcategorieën mogelijk "
"te maken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:38
msgid "Storage location setup"
msgstr "Instellen opslaglocaties"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:40
msgid ""
"Set up storage locations to work with the storage category. A parent "
"location must be set up, with child locations (or *sublocations*) assigned "
"to it. This is because the putaway rule's :ref:`Store to <inventory/routes/"
"set-putaway-attribute>` location will be set to the parent location, and "
"the :ref:`storage category <inventory/routes/assign-location>` will be set "
"to the child location."
msgstr ""
"Stel opslaglocaties in om met de opslagcategorie te werken. Er moet een "
"bovenliggende locatie worden ingesteld, met daaraan toegewezen onderliggende "
"locaties (of *sublocaties*). Dit komt doordat de :ref:`Opslaan naar "
"<inventory/routes/set-putaway-attribute>`-locatie van de wegzetregel wordt "
"ingesteld op de bovenliggende locatie, en de :ref:`opslagcategorie "
"<inventory/routes/assign-location>` wordt ingesteld op de onderliggende "
"locatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:45
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`."
msgstr "Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad app --> Configuratie --> Locaties`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:47
msgid ""
"First, set up a parent location. This can be as simple as the default `WH/"
"Stock` location. Alternatively, create a new parent location by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`New` button on the :guilabel:`Locations` page. On this parent "
"location form, specify a :guilabel:`Location Name` and :guilabel:`Parent "
"Location`. Select :guilabel:`Internal` as the :guilabel:`Location Type`."
msgstr ""
"Stel eerst een bovenliggende locatie in. Dit kan zo simpel zijn als de "
"standaard `WH/Stock`-locatie. Je kunt ook een nieuwe bovenliggende locatie "
"aanmaken door op de knop :guilabel:`Nieuw` te klikken op de pagina "
":guilabel:`Locaties`. Geef op dit formulier voor de bovenliggende locatie "
"een :guilabel:`Locatienaam` en :guilabel:`Bovenliggende locatie` op. "
"Selecteer :guilabel:`Intern` als het :guilabel:`Locatietype`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:52
msgid ""
"Then, create *sublocations* of this parent location by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`New` button. On the location form, specify "
"a :guilabel:`Location Name`, and set the :guilabel:`Parent Location` to the "
"parent location that was just created."
msgstr ""
"Maak vervolgens *sublocaties* van deze bovenliggende locatie aan door op de "
"knop :guilabel:`Nieuw` te klikken. Geef op het locatieformulier een "
":guilabel:`Locatienaam` op en stel de :guilabel:`Bovenliggende locatie` in "
"op de bovenliggende locatie die zojuist is aangemaakt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:57
msgid ""
"A beverage company stores all of its cans of lemonade on pallets in one "
"section of its warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Een drankenbedrijf bewaart al zijn blikjes limonade op pallets in één sectie "
"van zijn magazijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:59
msgid ""
"First, they create a location named `Pallets` in the `WH/Stock` location. "
"Then, they create two sublocations, named `PAL1` and `PAL2`. Both have `WH/"
"Stock/Pallets` set as the parent location."
msgstr ""
"Eerst maken ze een locatie met de naam `Pallets` aan in de locatie `WH/"
"Stock`. Vervolgens maken ze twee sublocaties aan met de namen `PAL1` en "
"`PAL2`. Beide hebben `WH/Stock/Pallets` ingesteld als bovenliggende locatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid "Create a sublocation."
msgstr "Maak een sublocatie aan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:68
msgid "Define storage category limitations"
msgstr "Definieer beperkingen van opslagcategorie"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:70
msgid ""
"Before a storage category is applied to locations, it must be configured "
"with specific limitations in order to decide the optimal storage location. "
"Capacity can be limited by weight, product, and package type."
msgstr ""
"Voordat een opslagcategorie op locaties wordt toegepast, moet deze worden "
"geconfigureerd met specifieke beperkingen om de optimale opslaglocatie te "
"bepalen. Capaciteit kan worden beperkt op gewicht, product en pakkettype."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:74
msgid ""
"To create a storage category, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Storage Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Opslagcategorieën` "
"en klik op :guilabel:`Nieuw` om een opslagcategorie aan te maken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:77
msgid ""
"On the storage category form, type a name for the category in "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Category` field."
msgstr "Typ in het veld :guilabel:`Opslagcategorie` een naam voor de categorie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:81
msgid ""
"Weight limits can be combined with capacity by package or product (e.g. a "
"maximum of one hundred products with a total weight of two hundred "
"kilograms)."
msgstr ""
"Gewichtslimieten kunnen worden gecombineerd met capaciteit per pakket of "
"product (bv. een maximum van honderd producten met een totaalgewicht van "
"tweehonderd kilogram)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:84
msgid ""
"While it is possible to limit capacity by product and package type at the "
"same location, it may be more practical to store items in different amounts "
"across various locations, as shown in the :ref:`limit capacity by package "
"<inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>` example."
msgstr ""
"Hoewel het mogelijk is om capaciteit te beperken op product en pakkettype op "
"dezelfde locatie, kan het praktischer zijn om artikelen in verschillende "
"hoeveelheden op verschillende locaties op te slaan, zoals getoond in het "
"voorbeeld :ref:`capaciteit beperken per pakket <inventory/routes/set-"
"capacity-package>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:88
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Allow New Product` field defines when the location is "
"considered available to store a product:"
msgstr ""
"Het veld :guilabel:`Nieuw product toestaan` bepaalt wanneer de locatie "
"beschikbaar wordt geacht om een product op te slaan:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If location is empty`: a product can be added there only if the "
"location is empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Als locatie leeg is`: een product kan daar alleen worden "
"toegevoegd als de locatie leeg is."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If products are the same`: a product can be added there only if "
"the same product is already there."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Als producten hetzelfde zijn`: een product kan daar alleen worden "
"toegevoegd als hetzelfde product er al is."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow mixed products`: several different products can be stored "
"in this location at the same time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gemengde producten toestaan`: verschillende producten kunnen "
"tegelijkertijd op deze locatie worden opgeslagen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:151
msgid ""
"Odoo does **not** automatically split quantities across multiple storage "
"locations. If an incoming receipt contains several units or packages and the "
"first recommended location exceeds its capacity, Odoo still routes all items "
"to that same location instead of selecting another one with available space."
msgstr ""
"Odoo splitst hoeveelheden **niet** automatisch over meerdere opslaglocaties. "
"Als een inkomende ontvangst meerdere eenheden of pakketten bevat en de "
"eerste aanbevolen locatie zijn capaciteit overschrijdt, routeert Odoo nog "
"steeds alle artikelen naar diezelfde locatie in plaats van een andere te "
"selecteren met beschikbare ruimte."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:156
msgid ""
"*(Example: If a location can hold 10 units and 12 units arrive, all 12 are "
"still assigned to that location.)*"
msgstr ""
"*(Voorbeeld: Als een locatie 10 eenheden kan bevatten en er 12 eenheden "
"aankomen, worden alle 12 nog steeds aan die locatie toegewezen.)*"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:107
msgid "Limit capacity by weight"
msgstr "Beperk capaciteit op gewicht"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:109
msgid ""
"A maximum product weight can be set in the :guilabel:`Max Weight` field. "
"This limit applies to each location assigned this storage category. If a "
"product weight is defined, the value must be set to greater than `0`."
msgstr ""
"Er kan een maximaal productgewicht worden ingesteld in het veld "
":guilabel:`Max. gewicht`. Deze limiet geldt voor elke locatie waaraan deze "
"opslagcategorie is toegewezen. Als een productgewicht is gedefinieerd, moet "
"de waarde worden ingesteld op groter dan `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:114
msgid "Limit capacity by product"
msgstr "Beperk capaciteit op product"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:116
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Capacity by Product` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` to "
"enter a product, and set the maximum capacity that should be stored at each "
"location in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik in het tabblad :guilabel:`Capaciteit per product` op :guilabel:`Voeg "
"een regel toe` om een product in te voeren en stel de maximale capaciteit in "
"die op elke locatie moet worden opgeslagen in het veld "
":guilabel:`Hoeveelheid`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:120
msgid ""
"To ensure only a maximum of five `Large Cabinets` and two `Corner Desk Right "
"Sit` are stored at a single storage location, specify those amounts in "
"the :guilabel:`Capacity by Product` tab."
msgstr ""
"Om ervoor te zorgen dat slechts maximaal vijf `Grote Kasten` en twee "
"`Hoekbureau Rechts Zit` op één opslaglocatie worden opgeslagen, geef je die "
"hoeveelheden op in het tabblad :guilabel:`Capaciteit per Product`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid "Show storage category limiting by product count."
msgstr "Toon opslagcategorie met beperking per productaantal."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:129
msgid "Limit capacity by package type"
msgstr "Capaciteit beperken per pakkettype"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:131
msgid ""
"Limiting capacity by :doc:`package <../../product_management/configure/"
"package>` makes it possible to enforce real-time storage capacity checks "
"based on package type (e.g., crates, bins, boxes, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Het beperken van de capaciteit per :doc:`pakket <../../product_management/"
"configure/package>` maakt het mogelijk om realtime "
"opslagcapaciteitscontroles af te dwingen op basis van pakkettype (bv. "
"kratten, bakken, dozen, enz.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:135
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a :ref:`package type <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/package-type>` to the storage category. Alternatively, "
"create a new package type on the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of the product "
"form (in the :guilabel:`Packaging` section), or from the :guilabel:`Product "
"Packagings` page."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Regel toevoegen` om een :ref:`pakkettype <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/package-type>` toe te voegen aan de opslagcategorie. Je "
"kunt ook een nieuw pakkettype aanmaken op het tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad` "
"van het productformulier (in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Verpakking`), of vanaf "
"de pagina :guilabel:`Productverpakkingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:141
msgid ""
"To help create putaway rules for pallet-stored items, create the `High "
"frequency pallets` storage category."
msgstr ""
"Maak de opslagcategorie `Hoogfrequente pallets` aan om wegzetregels te maken "
"voor op pallets opgeslagen artikelen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:144
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Capacity by Package` tab, specify the number of packages "
"for the designated :guilabel:`Package Type`, and set a maximum of `2.00` "
"`Pallets` for a specific location."
msgstr ""
"Geef in het tabblad :guilabel:`Capaciteit per pakket` het aantal pakketten "
"op voor het aangewezen :guilabel:`Pakkettype`, en stel een maximum in van "
"`2.00` `Pallets` voor een specifieke locatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid "Create a storage category."
msgstr "Maak een opslagcategorie aan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:162
msgid "Assign storage locations"
msgstr "Opslaglocaties toewijzen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:164
msgid ""
"After the storage category is created, it can be assigned to the "
"sublocations. Go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Locations`, and open the desired sublocation. Then, select the created "
"category in the :guilabel:`Storage Category` field."
msgstr ""
"Nadat de opslagcategorie is aangemaakt, kun je deze toewijzen aan de "
"sublocaties. Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Locaties` en open de gewenste sublocatie. Selecteer vervolgens de "
"aangemaakte categorie in het veld :guilabel:`Opslagcategorie`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:169
msgid ""
"Assign the `High frequency pallets` storage category (which limits pallets "
"stored at any location to two pallets) to the `WH/Stock/Pallets/PAL1` "
"sublocation."
msgstr ""
"Wijs de opslagcategorie `Hoogfrequente pallets` (die het aantal pallets dat "
"op een locatie kan worden opgeslagen beperkt tot twee pallets) toe aan de "
"sublocatie `WH/Voorraad/Pallets/PAL1`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid ""
"When a Storage Category is created, it can be linked to a warehouse location."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer een opslagcategorie is aangemaakt, kan deze worden gekoppeld aan een "
"magazijnlocatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:175
msgid ""
"Repeat this step for all sublocations to which the storage category should "
"apply."
msgstr ""
"Herhaal deze stap voor alle sublocaties waarop de opslagcategorie van "
"toepassing moet zijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:178
msgid ""
"On the storage category form, the :icon:`oi-arrows-v` :guilabel:`Locations` "
"smart button shows which storage locations the category has been assigned to."
msgstr ""
"Op het opslagcategorieformulier toont de slimme knop :icon:`oi-arrows-v` "
":guilabel:`Locaties` aan welke opslaglocaties de categorie is toegewezen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:184
msgid "Create a putaway rule"
msgstr "Maak een wegzetregel aan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:186
msgid ""
"With the :ref:`storage category <inventory/routes/define-storage>` "
"and :ref:`locations <inventory/routes/assign-location>` set up, create "
"the :doc:`putaway rule <putaway>` by navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Configuration --> Putaway Rules`."
msgstr ""
"Nu de :ref:`opslagcategorie <inventory/routes/define-storage>` en "
":ref:`locaties <inventory/routes/assign-location>` zijn ingesteld, maak je "
"de :doc:`wegzetregel <putaway>` aan door te navigeren naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Wegzetregels`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:190
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button to create the putaway rule. Specify a "
"location in the :guilabel:`Store to` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`Nieuw` om de wegzetregel aan te maken. Geef een "
"locatie op in het veld :guilabel:`Opslaan naar`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:193
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Sublocation` field to specify that you want to use a "
"storage category on the sublocations of the :guilabel:`Store to` field:"
msgstr ""
"Gebruik het veld :guilabel:`Sublocatie` om aan te geven dat je een "
"opslagcategorie wilt gebruiken op de sublocaties van het veld "
":guilabel:`Opslaan naar`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:196
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Last Used`: The last location that had a move associated with it "
"for that product or product category is used. If there is no last location "
"used, the destination is whatever is specified in the :guilabel:`Store to` "
"field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Laatst gebruikt`: De laatste locatie die een verplaatsing voor "
"dat product of die productcategorie had, wordt gebruikt. Als er geen laatst "
"gebruikte locatie is, is de bestemming wat er in het veld :guilabel:`Opslaan "
"naar` is opgegeven."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:199
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closest Location`: The locations specified as part of the storage "
"category are used. A storage category is mandatory in the :guilabel:`Having "
"Category` field. The locations in the storage category must be sublocations "
"of the location in the :guilabel:`Store to` field. If the closest locations "
"in the storage category are full, the :guilabel:`Store to` location is used."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dichtstbijzijnde Locatie`: De locaties die zijn opgegeven als "
"onderdeel van de opslagcategorie worden gebruikt. Een opslagcategorie is "
"verplicht in het veld :guilabel:`Met Categorie`. De locaties in de "
"opslagcategorie moeten sublocaties zijn van de locatie in het veld "
":guilabel:`Opslaan naar`. Als de dichtstbijzijnde locaties in de "
"opslagcategorie vol zijn, wordt de locatie :guilabel:`Opslaan naar` gebruikt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:205
msgid ""
"Continuing the example from above, the `High frequency pallets` storage "
"category is assigned to the putaway rule directing pallets of lemonade to "
"locations with the `High frequency pallets` storage category :ref:`assigned "
"to them <inventory/routes/assign-location>`."
msgstr ""
"Om het voorbeeld van hierboven voort te zetten: de opslagcategorie "
"`Hoogfrequente pallets` wordt toegewezen aan de opbergregel die pallets "
"limonade naar locaties stuurt waaraan de opslagcategorie `Hoogfrequente "
"pallets` :ref:`is toegewezen <inventory/routes/assign-location>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid "Storage Categories used in putaway rules."
msgstr "Opslagcategorieën die worden gebruikt in wegzetregels."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:213
msgid ""
"If products are not routing to secondary locations for a storage category "
"and a product weight is defined, verify that the storage "
"category's :guilabel:`Max Weight` value is set to a number greater than `0`."
msgstr ""
"Als producten niet naar secundaire locaties worden gerouteerd voor een "
"opslagcategorie en er een productgewicht is gedefinieerd, controleer dan of "
"de waarde :guilabel:`Max. gewicht` van de opslagcategorie is ingesteld op "
"een getal groter dan `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:218
msgid "Use case: limit capacity by package"
msgstr "Gebruikssituatie: capaciteit beperken per pakket"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:220
msgid ""
"To limit the capacity of a storage location by a specific number of "
"packages, :ref:`create a storage category with a Capacity By Package "
"<inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>`."
msgstr ""
"Beperk de capaciteit van een opslaglocatie door een specifiek aantal "
"pakketten door :ref:`een opslagcategorie met een capaciteit per pakket aan "
"te maken <inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:223
msgid ""
"Continuing the examples from above, the `High frequency pallets` storage "
"category is assigned to the `PAL1` and `PAL2` locations."
msgstr ""
"Aansluitend op de bovenstaande voorbeelden is de opslagcategorie "
"`Hoogfrequente pallets` toegewezen aan de locaties `PAL1` en `PAL2`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, :ref:`putaway rules <inventory/routes/putaway-rule>` are set, so that "
"any pallets received in the warehouse are directed to be stored in `PAL1` "
"and `PAL2` locations."
msgstr ""
"Vervolgens worden :ref:`wegzetregels <inventory/routes/putaway-rule>` "
"ingesteld, zodat alle pallets die in het magazijn worden ontvangen naar de "
"locaties `PAL1` en `PAL2` worden geleid om te worden opgeslagen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:229
msgid ""
"Depending on the number of pallets on-hand at each of the storage locations, "
"when two pallets of lemonade cans is received, the following scenarios "
"happen:"
msgstr ""
"Afhankelijk van het aantal pallets op voorraad bij elk van de "
"opslaglocaties, gebeurt het volgende wanneer twee pallets limonadeblikjes "
"worden ontvangen:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:232
msgid ""
"If `PAL1` and `PAL2` are empty, the pallet is redirected to `WH/Stock/"
"Pallets/PAL1`."
msgstr ""
"Als `PAL1` en `PAL2` leeg zijn, wordt de pallet omgeleid naar `WH/Stock/"
"Pallets/PAL1`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:233
msgid "If `PAL1` is full, the pallet is redirected to `WH/Stock/Pallets/PAL2`."
msgstr ""
"Als `PAL1` vol is, wordt de pallet omgeleid naar `WH/Stock/Pallets/PAL2`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:234
msgid ""
"If `PAL1` and `PAL2` are full, the pallet is redirected to `WH/Stock/"
"Pallets`."
msgstr ""
"Als `PAL1` en `PAL2` vol zijn, wordt de pallet omgeleid naar `WH/Stock/"
"Pallets`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:235
msgid ""
"If `PAL1` is partially full (for example, with one pallet), Odoo treats more "
"than one received pallet as a single pallet on the receipt. You must "
"manually separate the two pallets into separate storage locations. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Details` link to the right of the :guilabel:`Units` field, "
"and then in the :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` box, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`. Finally, split the receipt by quantity into separate locations, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Als `PAL1` gedeeltelijk vol is (bijvoorbeeld met één pallet), behandelt Odoo "
"meer dan één ontvangen pallet als één enkele pallet op de ontvangst. Je moet "
"de twee pallets handmatig scheiden naar aparte opslaglocaties. Klik op de "
"link :guilabel:`Details` rechts van het veld :guilabel:`Eenheden`, en klik "
"vervolgens in het vak :guilabel:`Gedetailleerde activiteiten` op "
":guilabel:`Een regel toevoegen`. Splits ten slotte de ontvangst per "
"hoeveelheid naar aparte locaties en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:0
msgid ""
"Update the Detailed Operations box to route pallets to the correct locations."
msgstr ""
"Werk het vak Gedetailleerde activiteiten bij om pallets naar de juiste "
"locaties te routeren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:3
msgid "Routes and push/pull rules"
msgstr "Routes en push/pull-regels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Routes* in Odoo control the movement of products between different "
"locations, whether internal or external, using push and pull rules. Once set "
"up, these rules help automate the logistics of product movement based on "
"specific conditions."
msgstr ""
"*Routes* in Odoo regelen de beweging van producten tussen verschillende "
"locaties, zowel intern als extern, met behulp van push- en pull-regels. "
"Eenmaal ingesteld, helpen deze regels de logistiek van productbewegingen te "
"automatiseren op basis van specifieke voorwaarden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:10
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: Routes <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qkhDUezyZuc>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo Tutorials: Routes <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qkhDUezyZuc>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`Standard routes in Odoo <../daily_operations>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Standaard routes in Odoo <../daily_operations>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:14
msgid ""
"Routes are applicable on products, product categories, shipping methods, and "
"on the sales order line."
msgstr ""
"Routes zijn van toepassing op producten, productcategorieën, verzendmethoden "
"en op de verkooporderregel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:18
msgid "About routes and terminology"
msgstr "Over routes en terminologie"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:20
msgid ""
"In a generic warehouse, there are receiving docks, a quality control area, "
"storage locations, picking and packing areas, and shipping docks. All "
"products go through all these locations. As the products move through the "
"locations, each location triggers the products' specified route and rules."
msgstr ""
"In een generiek magazijn zijn er ontvangstdokken, een "
"kwaliteitscontrolegebied, opslaglocaties, pick- en verpakkingsgebieden en "
"verzenddokken. Alle producten doorlopen al deze locaties. Terwijl de "
"producten door de locaties bewegen, activeert elke locatie de "
"gespecificeerde route en regels van de producten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a generic warehouse with stock and quality control area."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van een generiek magazijn met voorraad en kwaliteitscontrolegebied."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:29
msgid ""
"In this example, vendor trucks unload pallets of ordered products at the "
"receiving docks. Operators then scan the products in the receiving area. "
"Depending on the product's route and rules, some of these products are sent "
"to a quality control area (for example, products that are components used in "
"the manufacturing process), while others are directly stored in their "
"respective locations."
msgstr ""
"In dit voorbeeld lossen vrachtwagens van leveranciers pallets met bestelde "
"producten bij de ontvangstdokken. Operators scannen vervolgens de producten "
"in het ontvangstgebied. Afhankelijk van de route en regels van het product "
"worden sommige van deze producten naar een kwaliteitscontrolegebied gestuurd "
"(bijvoorbeeld producten die onderdelen zijn voor het productieproces), "
"terwijl andere direct op hun respectievelijke locaties worden opgeslagen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a generic push to rule when receiving products."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van een generieke push-to-regel bij het ontvangen van producten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:38
msgid ""
"Here is an example of a fulfillment route. In the morning, items are picked "
"for all the orders that need to be prepared during the day. These items are "
"picked from storage locations and moved to the picking area, close to where "
"the orders are packed. Then, the orders are packed in their respective "
"boxes, and conveyor belts bring them to the shipping docks, ready to be "
"delivered to customers."
msgstr ""
"Hier is een voorbeeld van een fulfillment-route. In de ochtend worden "
"artikelen gepickt voor alle orders die tijdens de dag voorbereid moeten "
"worden. Deze artikelen worden gepickt uit opslaglocaties en verplaatst naar "
"het pickgebied, dicht bij waar de orders worden verpakt. Vervolgens worden "
"de orders in hun respectievelijke dozen verpakt en worden ze via "
"transportbanden naar de verzenddokken gebracht, klaar om aan klanten te "
"worden geleverd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a generic pull from rule when preparing deliveries."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van een generieke pull-from-regel bij het voorbereiden van "
"leveringen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:48
msgid "Push rules"
msgstr "Push-regels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:50
msgid ""
"Push rules are used to *supply products into a storage locations* as soon as "
"they arrive at a specific receiving location."
msgstr ""
"Push-regels worden gebruikt om *producten naar een opslaglocatie te leveren* "
"zodra ze op een specifieke ontvangstlocatie aankomen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:54
msgid ""
"Push rules can only be triggered if there are no pull rules that have "
"already generated the product transfers."
msgstr ""
"Push-regels kunnen alleen worden geactiveerd als er geen pull-regels zijn "
"die de productoverboekingen al hebben gegenereerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:57
msgid ""
"In a :doc:`one-step receipt route <receipts_delivery_one_step>`, which uses "
"one push rule, when a product arrives in the warehouse, a push rule can "
"automatically transfer it to the *Storage Location*. Different push rules "
"can be applied to different products, allowing for customized storage "
"locations."
msgstr ""
"In een :doc:`eenstaps-ontvangstroute <receipts_delivery_one_step>` die één "
"push-regel gebruikt, kan een push-regel een product automatisch naar de "
"*Opslaglocatie* verplaatsen wanneer het in het magazijn aankomt. "
"Verschillende push-regels kunnen op verschillende producten worden "
"toegepast, waardoor aangepaste opslaglocaties mogelijk zijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:66
msgid "Rule for a Receive in one step route."
msgstr "Regel voor een route Ontvangen in één stap."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:66
msgid "Push rule for the 'Receive in one step' route."
msgstr "Push-regel voor de route 'Ontvangen in één stap'."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:68
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:90
msgid ""
"For more information about configuring rules, skip to the :ref:`Configure "
"rules section <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Voor meer informatie over het configureren van regels, ga naar de sectie "
":ref:`Regels configureren <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:72
msgid "Pull rules"
msgstr "Pull-regels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:74
msgid ""
"Pull rules trigger product moves on demand, such as a sales order or "
"a :doc:`need to restock <../../warehouses_storage/replenishment/"
"reordering_rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Pull-regels activeren productbewegingen op aanvraag, zoals een verkooporder "
"of een :doc:`noodzaak om aan te vullen <../../warehouses_storage/"
"replenishment/reordering_rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:77
msgid ""
"Pull rules work backward from the demand location. For example, in "
"a :ref:`two-step delivery <inventory/shipping_receiving/two-step-delivery>` "
"route, where items move from *Stock* to *Output* before being delivered to "
"the *Customer Location*, the pull rule first creates a transfer from "
"*Output* to the customer. If the product is not at *Output*, another pull "
"rule creates a transfer from *Stock* to *Output*. The warehouse workers then "
"process these transfers in the reverse order: picking, then shipping."
msgstr ""
"Pull-regels werken achteruit vanaf de vraaglocatie. Bijvoorbeeld, in een "
":ref:`tweestaps-leveringsroute <inventory/shipping_receiving/two-step-"
"delivery>` waar artikelen van *Voorraad* naar *Output* bewegen voordat ze "
"naar de *Klantlocatie* worden geleverd, creëert de pull-regel eerst een "
"transfer van *Output* naar de klant. Als het product niet bij *Output* is, "
"creëert een andere pull-regel een transfer van *Voorraad* naar *Output*. De "
"magazijnmedewerkers verwerken deze transfers vervolgens in omgekeerde "
"volgorde: eerst picken, dan verzenden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:88
msgid "Example pull rule."
msgstr "Voorbeeld pull-regel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:88
msgid "Pull rules for the 'Deliver in two steps' route."
msgstr "Pull-regels voor de route 'Leveren in twee stappen'."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:98
msgid ""
"Since *Routes* are a collection of *Push and Pull Rules*, Odoo helps you "
"manage advanced route configurations such as:"
msgstr ""
"Aangezien *Routes* een verzameling van *Push- en Pull-regels* zijn, helpt "
"Odoo je bij het beheren van geavanceerde routeconfiguraties zoals:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:101
msgid "Manage product manufacturing chains."
msgstr "Beheer productieketens van producten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:102
msgid "Manage default locations per product."
msgstr "Beheer standaardlocaties per product."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:103
msgid ""
"Define routes within the stock warehouse according to business needs, such "
"as quality control, after-sales services, or supplier returns."
msgstr ""
"Definieer routes binnen het voorraadmagazijn volgens de bedrijfsbehoeften, "
"zoals kwaliteitscontrole, after-sales services of retourzendingen aan "
"leveranciers."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:105
msgid ""
"Help rental management by generating automated return moves for rented "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Ondersteun verhuurbeheer door geautomatiseerde inleververplaatsingen te "
"genereren voor verhuursproducten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:107
msgid ""
"To configure a route for a product, first, open the :guilabel:`Inventory` "
"application and go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section, enable the :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` "
"feature and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Om een route voor een product te configureren, open je eerst de "
":guilabel:`Voorraad`-applicatie en ga je naar "
":menuselection:`Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Schakel vervolgens in de "
"sectie :guilabel:`Magazijn` de functie :guilabel:`Routes met meerdere "
"stappen` in en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "Activate the Multi-Step Routes feature in Odoo Inventory."
msgstr "Activeer de functie Routes met meerdere stappen in Odoo Voorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:116
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Storage Locations` feature is automatically activated with "
"the :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` feature."
msgstr ""
"De functie :guilabel:`Opslaglocaties` wordt automatisch geactiveerd met de "
"functie :guilabel:`Routes met meerdere stappen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:119
msgid ""
"Once this first step is completed, the user can use pre-configured routes "
"that come with Odoo, or they can create custom routes."
msgstr ""
"Zodra deze eerste stap is voltooid, kun je vooraf geconfigureerde routes "
"gebruiken die bij Odoo worden geleverd, of je kunt aangepaste routes maken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:123
msgid "Pre-configured routes"
msgstr "Voorgeconfigureerde routes"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:125
msgid ""
"To access Odoo's pre-configured routes, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Warehouses`. Then, open a warehouse form. In "
"the :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` tab, the user can view the "
"warehouse's pre-configured routes for :guilabel:`Incoming Shipments` "
"and :guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments`."
msgstr ""
"Om toegang te krijgen tot de vooraf geconfigureerde routes van Odoo, ga je "
"naar :menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Magazijnen`. Open "
"vervolgens een magazijnformulier. In het tabblad "
":guilabel:`Magazijnconfiguratie` kun je de vooraf geconfigureerde routes van "
"het magazijn bekijken voor :guilabel:`Inkomende verzendingen` en "
":guilabel:`Uitgaande verzendingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "A pre-configured warehouse in Odoo Inventory."
msgstr "Een vooraf geconfigureerd magazijn in Odoo Voorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:134
msgid ""
"Some more advanced routes, such as pick-pack-ship, are also available. The "
"user can select the route that best fits their business needs. Once "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming Shipments` and :guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments` routes "
"are set, head to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Routes` to "
"see the specific routes that Odoo generated."
msgstr ""
"Sommige meer geavanceerde routes, zoals pick-pack-ship, zijn ook "
"beschikbaar. Je kunt de route selecteren die het beste past bij je "
"bedrijfsbehoeften. Zodra de routes :guilabel:`Inkomende verzendingen` en "
":guilabel:`Uitgaande verzendingen` zijn ingesteld, ga je naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Routes` om de specifieke "
"routes te zien die Odoo heeft gegenereerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of all the preconfigured routes Odoo offers."
msgstr "Overzicht van alle vooraf geconfigureerde routes die Odoo biedt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:143
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Routes` page, click on a route to open the route form. In "
"the route form, the user can view which places the route "
"is :guilabel:`Applicable On`. The user can also set the route to only apply "
"on a specific :guilabel:`Company`. This is useful for multi-company "
"environments; for example, a user can have a company and warehouse in "
"Country A and a second company and warehouse in Country B."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de pagina :guilabel:`Routes` op een route om het routeformulier te "
"openen. In het routeformulier kun je bekijken waar de route "
":guilabel:`Toepasbaar op` is. Je kunt de route ook zo instellen dat deze "
"alleen van toepassing is op een specifiek :guilabel:`Bedrijf`. Dit is handig "
"voor multi-bedrijfsomgevingen; bijvoorbeeld, je kunt een bedrijf en magazijn "
"hebben in land A en een tweede bedrijf en magazijn in land B."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a route example applicable on product categories and warehouses."
msgstr ""
"Overzicht van een routevoorbeeld toepasbaar op productcategorieën en "
"magazijnen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:153
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the route form, the user can view the "
"specific :guilabel:`Rules` for the route. Each :guilabel:`Rule` has "
"an :guilabel:`Action`, a :guilabel:`Source Location`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Destination Location`."
msgstr ""
"Onderaan het routeformulier kun je de specifieke :guilabel:`Regels` voor de "
"route bekijken. Elke :guilabel:`Regel` heeft een :guilabel:`Actie`, een "
":guilabel:`Bronlocatie` en een :guilabel:`Bestemmingslocatie`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "An example of rules with push & pull actions in Odoo Inventory."
msgstr "Een voorbeeld van regels met push & pull-acties in Odoo Voorraad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:162
msgid "Custom Routes"
msgstr "Aangepaste routes"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:164
msgid ""
"To create a custom route, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration "
"--> Routes`, and click on :guilabel:`Create`. Next, choose the places where "
"this route can be selected. A route can be applicable on a combination of "
"places."
msgstr ""
"Om een aangepaste route te maken, ga je naar :menuselection:`Voorraad --> "
"Configuratie --> Routes` en klik je op :guilabel:`Aanmaken`. Kies vervolgens "
"de plaatsen waar deze route kan worden geselecteerd. Een route kan van "
"toepassing zijn op een combinatie van plaatsen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a pick-pack-ship route."
msgstr "Overzicht van een pick-pack-ship-route."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:172
msgid ""
"Each place has a different behavior, so it is important to tick only the "
"useful ones and adapt each route accordingly. Then, configure "
"the :guilabel:`Rules` of the route."
msgstr ""
"Elke plaats heeft een ander gedrag, dus het is belangrijk om alleen de "
"nuttige plaatsen aan te vinken en elke route dienovereenkomstig aan te "
"passen. Configureer vervolgens de :guilabel:`Regels` van de route."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:175
msgid ""
"If the route is applicable on a product category, the route still needs to "
"be manually set on the product category form by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Product Categories`. "
"Then, select the product category and open the form. Next, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` and under the :guilabel:`Logistics` section, set "
"the :guilabel:`Routes`."
msgstr ""
"Als de route van toepassing is op een productcategorie, moet de route nog "
"steeds handmatig worden ingesteld op het productcategorieformulier door naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Productcategorieën` te gaan. "
"Selecteer vervolgens de productcategorie en open het formulier. Klik daarna "
"op :guilabel:`Bewerken` en stel onder de sectie :guilabel:`Logistiek` de "
":guilabel:`Routes` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:180
msgid ""
"When applying the route on a product category, all the rules configured in "
"the route are applied to **every** product in the category. This can be "
"helpful if the business uses the dropshipping process for all the products "
"from the same category."
msgstr ""
"Bij het toepassen van de route op een productcategorie worden alle regels "
"die in de route zijn geconfigureerd, toegepast op **elk** product in de "
"categorie. Dit kan handig zijn als het bedrijf het dropshipping-proces "
"gebruikt voor alle producten uit dezelfde categorie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a route applied to the \"all\" product category."
msgstr "Weergave van een route toegepast op de productcategorie \"alles\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:188
msgid ""
"The same behavior applies to the warehouses. If the route can apply "
"to :guilabel:`Warehouses`, all the transfers occurring inside the chosen "
"warehouse that meet the conditions of the route's rules will then follow "
"that route."
msgstr ""
"Hetzelfde gedrag geldt voor de magazijnen. Als de route kan worden toegepast "
"op :guilabel:`Magazijnen`, volgen alle overboekingen binnen het gekozen "
"magazijn die voldoen aan de voorwaarden van de regels van de route, deze "
"route."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the warehouse drop-down menu when selecting applicable on warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van het vervolgkeuzemenu voor magazijnen bij het selecteren van "
"toepasbaar op magazijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:196
msgid ""
"If the route is applicable on :guilabel:`Sales Order Lines`, it is more or "
"less the opposite. The route must be manually chosen when creating a "
"quotation. This is useful if some products go through different routes."
msgstr ""
"Als de route toepasbaar is op :guilabel:`Verkooporderregels`, is het min of "
"meer het tegenovergestelde. De route moet handmatig worden gekozen bij het "
"maken van een offerte. Dit is handig als sommige producten via verschillende "
"routes gaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:200
msgid ""
"Remember to toggle the visibility of the :guilabel:`Route` column on the "
"quotation/sales order. Then, the route can be chosen on each line of the "
"quotation/sales order."
msgstr ""
"Vergeet niet de zichtbaarheid van de kolom :guilabel:`Route` in de offerte/"
"verkooporder in te schakelen. Vervolgens kan de route op elke regel van de "
"offerte/verkooporder worden gekozen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of the menu allowing to add new lines to sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van het menu waarmee nieuwe regels aan verkooporders kunnen worden "
"toegevoegd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:207
msgid ""
"Finally, there are routes that can be applied to products. Those work more "
"or less like the product categories: once selected, the route must be "
"manually set on the product form."
msgstr ""
"Tot slot zijn er routes die kunnen worden toegepast op producten. Deze "
"werken min of meer zoals de productcategorieën: eenmaal geselecteerd moet de "
"route handmatig op het productformulier worden ingesteld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:210
msgid ""
"To set a route on a product, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --"
"> Products` and select the desired product. Then, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab and under the :guilabel:`Operations` section, "
"select the :guilabel:`Routes`."
msgstr ""
"Stel een route in op een product via :menuselection:`Voorraad --> "
"Producten --> Producten` en selecteer het gewenste product. Ga vervolgens "
"naar het tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad` en selecteer onder het gedeelte "
":guilabel:`Bewerkingen` de :guilabel:`Routes`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of a product form, where the route must be selected."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van een productformulier, waar de route moet worden geselecteerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:219
msgid "Rules must be set on the route in order for the route to work."
msgstr "Stel regels in op de route om de route te laten werken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:224
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Regels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:226
msgid ""
"The rules are defined on the route form. First, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Routes` and open the "
"desired route form. Next, click :guilabel:`Edit` and in "
"the :guilabel:`Rules` section, click on :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Definieer de regels op het routeformulier. Ga eerst naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Routes` en open het gewenste "
"routeformulier. Klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Bewerken` en klik in het "
"gedeelte :guilabel:`Regels` op :guilabel:`Regel toevoegen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of the rules menu, where it is possible to add new rules."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van het regelmenu, waar het mogelijk is om nieuwe regels toe te "
"voegen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:234
msgid ""
"The available rules trigger various actions. If Odoo offers *Push* and "
"*Pull* rules, others are also available. Each rule has an :guilabel:`Action`:"
msgstr ""
"De beschikbare regels activeren verschillende acties. Als Odoo *Push*- en "
"*Pull*-regels biedt, zijn er ook andere beschikbaar. Elke regel heeft een "
":guilabel:`Actie`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pull From`: this rule is triggered by a need for the product in a "
"specific location. The need can come from a sales order being validated or "
"from a manufacturing order requiring a specific component. When the need "
"appears in the destination location, Odoo generates a picking to fulfill "
"this need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pull van`: deze regel wordt geactiveerd door een behoefte aan het "
"product op een specifieke locatie. De behoefte kan voortkomen uit een "
"gevalideerde verkooporder of uit een productieorder die een specifiek "
"onderdeel vereist. Wanneer de behoefte verschijnt op de bestemmingslocatie, "
"genereert Odoo een picking om aan deze behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Push To`: this rule is triggered by the arrival of some products "
"in the defined source location. In the case of the user moving products to "
"the source location, Odoo generates a picking to move those products to the "
"destination location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Push naar`: deze regel wordt geactiveerd door de aankomst van "
"producten op de gedefinieerde bronlocatie. Als de gebruiker producten naar "
"de bronlocatie verplaatst, genereert Odoo een picking om die producten naar "
"de bestemmingslocatie te verplaatsen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:244
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pull & Push`: this rule allows the generation of pickings in the "
"two situations explained above. This means that when products are required "
"at a specific location, a transfer is created from the previous location to "
"fulfill that need. This creates a need in the previous location and a rule "
"is triggered to fulfill it. Once the second need is fulfilled, the products "
"are pushed to the destination location and all the needs are fulfilled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pull & Push`: deze regel maakt het mogelijk om pickings te "
"genereren in de twee hierboven uitelegde situaties. Dit betekent dat wanneer "
"producten op een specifieke locatie nodig zijn, een transfer wordt "
"aangemaakt vanaf de vorige locatie om aan die behoefte te voldoen. Dit "
"creëert een behoefte op de vorige locatie en een regel wordt geactiveerd om "
"hieraan te voldoen. Zodra aan de tweede behoefte is voldaan, worden de "
"producten naar de bestemmingslocatie gepusht en is aan alle behoeften "
"voldaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:249
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy`: when products are needed at the destination location, a "
"request for quotation is created to fulfill the need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kopen`: wanneer producten nodig zijn op de bestemmingslocatie, "
"wordt een offerteaanvraag aangemaakt om aan de behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:251
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manufacture`: when products are needed in the source location, a "
"manufacturing order is created to fulfill the need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produceren`: wanneer producten nodig zijn op de bronlocatie, "
"wordt een productieorder aangemaakt om aan de behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Overview of a \"Pull From\" rule that creates a transfer between the stock "
"and the packing\n"
"zone."
msgstr ""
"Overzicht van een \"Pull van\"-regel die een transfer creëert tussen de "
"voorraad en de verpakkingszone."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:259
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Operation Type` must also be defined on the rule. This "
"defines which kind of picking is created from the rule."
msgstr ""
"Definieer ook het :guilabel:`Bewerkingstype` op de regel. Dit bepaalt welk "
"type picking wordt aangemaakt vanuit de regel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:262
msgid ""
"If the rule's :guilabel:`Action` is set to :guilabel:`Pull From` "
"or :guilabel:`Pull & Push`, a :guilabel:`Supply Method` must be set. "
"The :guilabel:`Supply Method` defines what happens at the source location:"
msgstr ""
"Als de :guilabel:`Actie` van de regel is ingesteld op :guilabel:`Pullen van` "
"of :guilabel:`Pullen & pushen`, moet een :guilabel:`Bevoorradingsmethode` "
"worden ingesteld. De :guilabel:`Bevoorradingsmethode` bepaalt wat er gebeurt "
"op de bronlocatie:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:266
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Take From Stock`: the products are taken from the available stock "
"of the source location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nemen uit voorraad`: de producten worden genomen uit de "
"beschikbare voorraad van de bronlocatie."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:268
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Trigger Another Rule`: the system tries to find a stock rule to "
"bring the products to the source location. The available stock is ignored."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Activeer een andere regel`: het systeem probeert een voorraad "
"regel te vinden om de producten naar de bronlocatie te brengen. De "
"beschikbare voorraad wordt genegeerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:270
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Take From Stock, if Unavailable, Trigger Another Rule`: the "
"products are taken from the available stock of the source location. If there "
"is no stock available, the system tries to find a rule to bring the products "
"to the source location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nemen uit voorraad, indien niet beschikbaar, activeer een andere "
"regel`: de producten worden genomen uit de beschikbare voorraad van de "
"bronlocatie. Als er geen voorraad beschikbaar is, probeert het systeem een "
"regel te vinden om de producten naar de bronlocatie te brengen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:275
msgid "Example flow"
msgstr "Voorbeeldstroom"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:277
msgid ""
"In this example, let's use a custom *Pick - Pack - Ship* route to try a full "
"flow with an advanced custom route."
msgstr ""
"In dit voorbeeld gebruiken we een aangepaste *Picken - Inpakken - Verzenden* "
"route om een volledige stroom met een geavanceerde aangepaste route te "
"proberen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:280
msgid ""
"First, a quick look at the route's rules and their supply methods. There are "
"three rules, all :guilabel:`Pull From` rules. The :guilabel:`Supply Methods` "
"for each rule are the following:"
msgstr ""
"Eerst een snelle blik op de regels van de route en hun "
"bevoorradingsmethoden. Er zijn drie regels, allemaal :guilabel:`Pullen van` "
"regels. De :guilabel:`Bevoorradingsmethoden` voor elke regel zijn de "
"volgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:283
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Take From Stock`: When products are needed in the :guilabel:`WH/"
"Packing Zone`, *picks* (internal transfers from :guilabel:`WH/Stock` "
"to :guilabel:`WH/Packing Zone`) are created from :guilabel:`WH/Stock` to "
"fulfill the need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nemen uit voorraad`: wanneer producten nodig zijn in de "
":guilabel:`WH/Inpakzone`, worden *picks* (interne verplaatsingen van "
":guilabel:`WH/Voorraad` naar :guilabel:`WH/Inpakzone`) aangemaakt vanuit "
":guilabel:`WH/Voorraad` om aan de behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:286
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Trigger Another Rule`: When products are needed in :guilabel:`WH/"
"Output`, *packs* (internal transfers from :guilabel:`WH/Packing Zone` "
"to :guilabel:`WH/Output`) are created from :guilabel:`WH/Packing Zone` to "
"fulfill the need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Activeer een andere regel`: wanneer producten nodig zijn in "
":guilabel:`WH/Output`, worden *packs* (interne verplaatsingen van "
":guilabel:`WH/Inpakzone` naar :guilabel:`WH/Output`) aangemaakt vanuit "
":guilabel:`WH/Inpakzone` om aan de behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:289
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Trigger Another Rule`: When products are needed "
"in :guilabel:`Partner Locations/Customers`, *delivery orders* are created "
"from :guilabel:`WH/Output` to fulfill the need."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Activeer een andere regel`: wanneer producten nodig zijn in "
":guilabel:`Partnerlocaties/Klanten`, worden *leveringsorders* aangemaakt "
"vanuit :guilabel:`WH/Output` om aan de behoefte te voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "Overview of all the transfers created by the pick - pack - ship route."
msgstr ""
"Overzicht van alle verplaatsingen die zijn aangemaakt door de picken - "
"inpakken - verzenden route."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:297
msgid ""
"This means that, when a customer orders products that have a *pick - pack - "
"ship* route set on it, a delivery order is created to fulfill the order."
msgstr ""
"Dit betekent dat wanneer een klant producten bestelt waarvoor een *picken - "
"inpakken - verzenden* route is ingesteld, een leveringsorder wordt "
"aangemaakt om de order te vervullen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of the operations created by a pull from transfer."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van de activiteiten die zijn aangemaakt door een pull from "
"verplaatsing."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:305
msgid ""
"If the source document for multiple tranfers is the same sales order, the "
"status is not the same. The status will be :guilabel:`Waiting Another "
"Operation` if the previous transfer in the list is not done yet."
msgstr ""
"Als het brondocument voor meerdere verplaatsingen dezelfde verkooporder is, "
"is de status niet hetzelfde. De status is :guilabel:`Wacht op een andere "
"bewerking` als de vorige verplaatsing in de lijst nog niet is voltooid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the transfers' various statuses at the beginning of the process."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van de verschillende statussen van de verplaatsingen aan het begin "
"van het proces."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:313
msgid ""
"To prepare the delivery order, packed products are needed at the output "
"area, so an internal transfer is requested from the packing zone."
msgstr ""
"Om de leveringsorder voor te bereiden zijn verpakte producten nodig in de "
"outputzone, dus wordt een interne verplaatsing aangevraagd vanuit de "
"inpakzone."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the detailed operations for a transfer between the packing and "
"output zones."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van de gedetailleerde activiteiten voor een verplaatsing tussen de "
"inpak- en outputzones."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:320
msgid ""
"Obviously, the packing zone needs products ready to be packed. So, an "
"internal transfer is requested to the stock and employees can gather the "
"required products from the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Uiteraard heeft de verpakkingszone producten nodig die klaar zijn om verpakt "
"te worden. Er wordt dus een interne transfer naar de voorraad aangevraagd en "
"werknemers kunnen de benodigde producten uit het magazijn verzamelen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the detailed operations for a transfer between the stock and packing "
"zones."
msgstr ""
"Weergave van de gedetailleerde activiteiten voor een verplaatsing tussen de "
"voorraad- en inpakzones."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:327
msgid ""
"As explained in the introduction of the documentation, the last step in the "
"process (for this route, the delivery order) is the first to be triggered, "
"which then triggers other rules until we reach the first step in the process "
"(here, the internal transfer from the stock to the packing area). Now, "
"everything is ready to be processed so the customer can get the ordered "
"items."
msgstr ""
"Zoals uitgelegd in de introductie van de documentatie is de laatste stap in "
"het proces (voor deze route, de leveringsorder) de eerste die wordt "
"geactiveerd, die vervolgens andere regels activeert totdat we de eerste stap "
"in het proces bereiken (hier, de interne verplaatsing van de voorraad naar "
"de inpakruimte). Nu is alles klaar om te worden verwerkt zodat de klant de "
"bestelde artikelen kan ontvangen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:332
msgid ""
"In this example, the product is delivered to the customer when all the rules "
"have been triggered and the transfers are done."
msgstr ""
"In dit voorbeeld wordt het product aan de klant geleverd wanneer alle regels "
"zijn geactiveerd en de verplaatsingen zijn voltooid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes.rst:None
msgid "View of the transfers' statuses when the route is completed."
msgstr "Weergave van de overboekingsstatussen wanneer de route voltooid is."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:3
msgid "Batch picking"
msgstr "Batchpicking"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:7
msgid ""
"*Batch picking* enables a single picker to handle multiple orders at once, "
"reducing the number of times needed to navigate to a warehouse location. "
"When picking in batches, orders are grouped and consolidated into a picking "
"list. After the picking, the batch is taken to an output location, where the "
"products are sorted into their respective delivery packages."
msgstr ""
"*Batchpicken* stelt één picker in staat meerdere bestellingen tegelijk af te "
"handelen, waardoor het aantal keren dat naar een magazijnlocatie genavigeerd "
"moet worden, wordt verminderd. Bij batchpicken worden bestellingen "
"gegroepeerd en samengevoegd in een picklijst. Na het picken wordt de batch "
"naar een outputlocatie gebracht, waar de producten in hun respectieve "
"leveringspakketten worden gesorteerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:12
msgid ""
"Since orders *must* be sorted at the output location after being picked, "
"this picking method suits businesses with a few products that are ordered "
"often. Storing high-demand items in easily accessible locations can increase "
"the number of orders that are fulfilled efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Aangezien bestellingen na het picken *moeten* worden gesorteerd op de "
"outputlocatie, is deze pickmethode geschikt voor bedrijven met een paar "
"producten die vaak besteld worden. Het opslaan van vaak gevraagde artikelen "
"op gemakkelijk toegankelijke locaties kan het aantal bestellingen dat "
"efficiënt wordt afgehandeld, verhogen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:16
msgid ""
"Batch picking is ideal for industries or warehouses that handle high order "
"volumes with a stable demand. This method increases efficiency by allowing "
"workers to pick items for multiple orders in one trip through the warehouse, "
"reducing travel time and boosting productivity."
msgstr ""
"Batchpicken is ideaal voor bedrijfstakken of magazijnen die grote "
"bestelhoeveelheden met een stabiele vraag verwerken. Deze methode verhoogt "
"de efficiëntie doordat medewerkers artikelen voor meerdere bestellingen in "
"één trip door het magazijn kunnen picken, waardoor de reistijd wordt verkort "
"en de productiviteit wordt verhoogd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:23
msgid ""
"To activate the batch picking option, begin by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` section, check the :guilabel:`Batch, Wave & "
"Cluster Transfers` box."
msgstr ""
"Activeer de batchpickoptie door naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen` te gaan. Vink onder de sectie "
":guilabel:`Bewerkingen` het vakje :guilabel:`Batch-, golf- en "
"clusterverplaatsingen` aan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:None
msgid "Enable the *Batch Transfers* in Inventory > Configuration > Settings."
msgstr ""
"Schakel de *Batchverplaatsingen* in via Voorraad > Configuratie > "
"Instellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/picking_methods/batch.rst:30
msgid ""
"Since batch picking is a method to optimize the *pick* operation in Odoo, "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` options "
"under the :guilabel:`Warehouse` heading must also be checked on this "
"settings page. When finished, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Aangezien batchpicken een methode is om de *pick*-activiteit in Odoo te "
"optimaliseren, moeten de opties :guilabel:`Opslaglocaties` en "
":guilabel:`Meerstapsroutes` onder de kop :guilabel:`Magazijn` ook op deze "
"instellingenpagina aangevinkt worden. Klik wanneer je klaar bent op "
":guilabel:`Opslaan`."

