msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Marge op tarief` is `10%` en :guilabel:`Extra marge` is `€9,00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show example of \"Based on rules\" shipping method with margins configured."
msgstr ""
"Toon een voorbeeld van de verzendmethode \"Op basis van regels\" met "
"geconfigureerde marges."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:172
