msgstr ":guilabel:`Adres`: `My Company (San Francisco)`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:66
msgid ""
"Notice how the inputs for the :guilabel:`Warehouse` field, for both the Odoo "
"configuration and the Sendcloud configuration, are the exact same."
msgstr ""
"Merk op dat de invoer voor het :guilabel:`Magazijn`-veld, zowel voor de Odoo-"
"configuratie als voor de Sendcloud-configuratie, exact hetzelfde is."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:70
msgid "Generate Sendcloud credentials"
msgstr "Sendcloud-inloggegevens genereren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:72
msgid ""
"In the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Integrations` in the menu on the right. Next, search for :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Native`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Ga in de Sendcloud-rekening naar :menuselection:`Instellingen --> "
"Integraties` in het menu aan de rechterkant. Zoek vervolgens naar "
":guilabel:`Odoo Native`. Klik daarna op :guilabel:`Verbinden`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:75
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Connect`, the page redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud API` settings page, where the :guilabel:`Public and "
"Secret Keys` are produced. The next step is to name "
"the :guilabel:`Integration`. The naming convention is as follows: `Odoo "
"CompanyName`, with the user's company name replacing `CompanyName` (e.g. "
"`Odoo StealthyWood`)."
msgstr ""
"Nadat je op :guilabel:`Verbinden` hebt geklikt, leidt de pagina door naar de "
":guilabel:`Sendcloud API`-instellingenpagina, waar de :guilabel:`Openbare en "
"geheime sleutels` worden gegenereerd. De volgende stap is het benoemen van "
"de :guilabel:`Integratie`. De naamgevingsconventie is als volgt: `Odoo "
"BedrijfsNaam`, waarbij de bedrijfsnaam van de gebruiker `BedrijfsNaam` "
"vervangt (bv. `Odoo StealthyWood`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:80
msgid ""
"Then, check the box next to :guilabel:`Service Points` and select the "
"shipping services for this integration. After saving, the :guilabel:`Public "
"and Secret Keys` are generated."
msgstr ""
"Vink vervolgens het vakje naast :guilabel:`Afhaalpunten` aan en selecteer de "
"verzendservices voor deze integratie. Na het opslaan worden de "
":guilabel:`Openbare en geheime sleutels` gegenereerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Configuring the Sendcloud integration and receiving the credentials."
msgstr "De Sendcloud-integratie configureren en de inloggegevens ontvangen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:90
msgid ""
"To ensure seamless Sendcloud integration with Odoo, :ref:`install <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` and :ref:`link <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` the Sendcloud shipping connector "
"to the Sendcloud account. Then, :ref:`configure Odoo fields <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, so Sendcloud can accurately "
"pull shipping data to generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Om een naadloze Sendcloud-integratie met Odoo te garanderen, "
":ref:`installeer <inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` en "
":ref:`koppel <inventory/shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` de "
"Sendcloud-verzendconnector aan de Sendcloud-rekening. :ref:`Configureer "
"vervolgens de Odoo-velden <inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-"
"info>`, zodat Sendcloud nauwkeurig verzendgegevens kan ophalen om labels te "
"genereren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:98
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable pickup points on websites <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-pickups>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Afhaalpunten op websites inschakelen <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-pickups>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:103
msgid "Install Sendcloud shipping module"
msgstr "Sendcloud-verzendmodule installeren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:105
msgid ""
"After the Sendcloud account is set up and configured, it's time to configure "
"the Odoo database. To get started, go to Odoo's :guilabel:`Apps` module, "
"search for the `Sendcloud Shipping` integration, and install it."
msgstr ""
"Nadat de Sendcloud-rekening is ingesteld en geconfigureerd, is het tijd om "
"de Odoo-database te configureren. Ga om aan de slag te gaan naar de "
":guilabel:`Apps`-module van Odoo, zoek naar de `Sendcloud Shipping`-"
"integratie en installeer deze."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Sendcloud Shipping module in the Odoo Apps module."
msgstr "Sendcloud-verzendmodule in de Odoo Apps-module."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:116
msgid "Sendcloud shipping connector configuration"
msgstr "Configuratie van Sendcloud-verzendingsconnector"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping` module "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"The :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector` setting is found under "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` section."
msgstr ""
"Activeer na installatie de module :guilabel:`Sendcloud-verzending` in "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`. De instelling "
":guilabel:`Sendcloud-connector` vind je onder het gedeelte "
":guilabel:`Verzendconnectoren`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:122
msgid ""
"After activating the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector`, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Klik na het activeren van de :guilabel:`Sendcloud-connector` op de link "
":guilabel:`Sendcloud-verzendingsmethoden` onder de vermelde connector. Klik "
"op de pagina :guilabel:`Verzendingsmethoden` op :guilabel:`Nieuw`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Shipping "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Verzendingsmethoden` zijn ook toegankelijk via "
":menuselection:`Voorraad --> Configuratie --> levering --> "
"Verzendingsmethoden`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:130
msgid ""
"Fill out the following fields in the :guilabel:`New Shipping Method` form:"
msgstr ""
"Vul de volgende velden in op het formulier :guilabel:`Nieuwe "
"verzendingsmethode`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:132
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: type `Sendcloud DPD`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Verzendingsmethode`: typ `Sendcloud DPD`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Sendcloud` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: selecteer :guilabel:`Sendcloud` uit het "
"vervolgkeuzemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: set the product that was configured for this "
"shipping method or create a new product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Leveringsproduct`: stel het product in dat voor deze "
"verzendingsmethode is geconfigureerd of maak een nieuw product aan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:136
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Public Key`."
msgstr ""
"Voer in het tabblad :guilabel:`SendCloud-configuratie` de "
":guilabel:`Openbare sleutel van Sendcloud` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:137
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Secret Key`."
msgstr ""
"Voer in het tabblad :guilabel:`SendCloud-configuratie` de :guilabel:`Geheime "
"sleutel van Sendcloud` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:142
msgid "Pickup points"
msgstr "Afhaalpunten"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:144
msgid ""
"Sendcloud's `service point delivery <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ lets customers choose a pickup "
"location (such as a nearby shop or locker) instead of entering a private "
"delivery address."
msgstr ""
"Met de `afhaalpuntenlevering van Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/"
"en-us/articles/360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ kunnen klanten een "
"afhaallocatie (zoals een winkel of kluisje in de buurt) kiezen in plaats van "
"een privébezorgadres in te voeren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:149
msgid ""
"To enable the feature, go to the shipping method form, and in "
"the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, under the :guilabel:`Options` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud Locations` feature."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar het verzendingsmethodeformulier om de functie in te schakelen en "
"schakel in het tabblad :guilabel:`SendCloud-configuratie` onder het gedeelte "
":guilabel:`Opties` de functie :guilabel:`Sendcloud-locaties gebruiken` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:154
msgid ""
"Pickup point selection is only available through the **Website** app (the "
"online checkout view). It is not currently possible to select a pickup point "
"manually through the **Sales** app (the internal database view)."
msgstr ""
"Selectie van afhaalpunten is alleen beschikbaar via de app **Website** (de "
"online afrekenweergave). Het is momenteel niet mogelijk om handmatig een "
"ophaalpunt te selecteren via de app **Verkoop** (de interne databaseweergave)"
"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:158
msgid ""
"For example, if the customer selects a shipping method like *Sendcloud "
"Mondial Relay*, they must choose a pickup point during the checkout process "
"on the website. If no pickup point is selected, the delivery order cannot be "
"validated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Als de klant bijvoorbeeld een verzendingsmethode zoals *Sendcloud Mondial "
"Relay* selecteert, moet hij tijdens het afrekenproces op de website een "
"ophaalpunt kiezen. Als er geen ophaalpunt is geselecteerd, kan de "
"leveringsorder niet worden gevalideerd in Odoo."

