msgid "Example of shipping products configured in Odoo."
msgstr "Voorbeeld van verzendproducten geconfigureerd in Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:199
msgid ""
"Sendcloud does not provide test keys when a company tests the sending of a "
"package in Odoo. This means if a package is created, the configured "
"Sendcloud account will be charged, unless the associated package is "
"cancelled within 24 hours of creation."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud biedt geen testsleutels wanneer een bedrijf het verzenden van een "
"pakket in Odoo test. Dit betekent dat als een pakket wordt aangemaakt, de "
"geconfigureerde Sendcloud-rekening wordt belast, tenzij het bijbehorende "
"pakket binnen 24 uur na aanmaak wordt geannuleerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:203
msgid ""
"Odoo has a built-in layer of protection against unwanted charges when using "
"test environments. Within a test environment, if a shipping method is used "
"to create labels, then those labels are immediately cancelled after the "
"creation — this occurs automatically. The test and production environment "
"settings can be toggled back and forth from their respective smart buttons."
msgstr ""
"Odoo heeft een ingebouwde beschermingslaag tegen ongewenste kosten bij het "
"gebruik van testomgevingen. Binnen een testomgeving worden labels, als een "
"verzendmethode wordt gebruikt om ze aan te maken, automatisch geannuleerd "
"direct na het aanmaken. De test- en productieomgevingsinstellingen kunnen "
"heen en weer worden geschakeld via hun respectieve knoppen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:213
msgid ""
"To use Sendcloud to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Om Sendcloud te gebruiken voor het genereren van verzendlabels, moet de "
"volgende informatie **volledig** en nauwkeurig worden ingevuld in Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:216
msgid ""
"**Customer information**: when creating a quotation, ensure the "
"selected :guilabel:`Customer` has a valid phone number, email address, and "
"shipping address."
msgstr ""
"**Klantinformatie**: zorg er bij het maken van een offerte voor dat de "
"geselecteerde :guilabel:`Klant` een geldig telefoonnummer, e-mailadres en "
"bezorgadres heeft."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:223
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: ensure all products in an order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of their "
"product form. Refer to the :ref:`Product weight section <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` of this article for detailed "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Productgewicht**: zorg ervoor dat alle producten in een bestelling een "
"gespecificeerd :guilabel:`Gewicht` hebben in het tabblad "
":guilabel:`Voorraad` van hun productformulier. Raadpleeg de :ref:`sectie "
"over productgewicht <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` van dit "
"artikel voor gedetailleerde instructies."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:227
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: ensure the warehouse name and address in Odoo match "
"the :ref:`previously defined warehouse <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-warehouse-config>` in the Sendcloud setup. For details on "
"warehouse configuration in Odoo, refer to the :ref:`warehouse configuration "
"section <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` of the "
"third-party shipping documentation."
msgstr ""
"**Magazijnadres**: zorg ervoor dat de magazijnnaam en het adres in Odoo "
"overeenkomen met het :ref:`eerder gedefinieerde magazijn <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-warehouse-config>` in de Sendcloud-setup. Voor "
"details over magazijnconfiguratie in Odoo, raadpleeg de :ref:`sectie over "
"magazijnconfiguratie <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>"
"` van de documentatie over externe verzending."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:234
msgid "Generate labels with Sendcloud"
msgstr "Labels genereren met Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:236
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add shipping and a :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"shipping product`. Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label "
"documents are automatically generated in the chatter, which include the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Wanneer je een offerte aanmaakt in Odoo, voeg verzending en een "
":guilabel:`Sendcloud-verzendproduct` toe. :guilabel:`Valideer` vervolgens de "
"levering. Verzendlabeldocumenten worden automatisch gegenereerd in de "
"chatter, waaronder het volgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Return label(s)` if the Sendcloud connector is configured for "
"returns."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Retourlabel(s)` als de Sendcloud-connector is geconfigureerd voor "
"retourzendingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customs document(s)` should the destination country require them."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Douanedocument(en)` als het bestemmingsland deze vereist."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:247
msgid ""
"When return labels are created, Sendcloud automatically charges the "
"configured Sendcloud account."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer retourlabels worden aangemaakt, brengt Sendcloud automatisch kosten "
"in rekening bij de geconfigureerde Sendcloud-rekening."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:250
msgid "Shipping rules"
msgstr "Verzendregels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:252
msgid ""
"Optionally, create shipping rules to automatically generate shipping labels "
"tailored to different product needs. For example, a shipping rule can be "
"created for customers shipping expensive jewelry items to purchase insurance."
msgstr ""
"Maak optioneel verzendregels aan om automatisch verzendlabels te genereren "
"die zijn afgestemd op verschillende productbehoeften. Er kan bijvoorbeeld "
"een verzendregel worden aangemaakt voor klanten die dure sieraden verzenden "
"om een verzekering af te sluiten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:257
msgid ""
"Shipping rules do **not** affect :ref:`shipping rate calculations <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, and are only used to improve the "
"process of :doc:`generating shipping labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"Verzendregels hebben **geen** invloed op :ref:`berekeningen van "
"verzendtarieven <inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>` en worden "
"alleen gebruikt om het proces van :doc:`het genereren van verzendlabels "
"<labels>` te verbeteren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:261
msgid ""
"To use shipping rules, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Delivery: Shipping Methods`, and select the intended "
"`Sendcloud` shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Om verzendregels te gebruiken, navigeer je naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-"
"app --> Configuratie --> Levering: Verzendmethoden` en selecteer je de "
"beoogde `Sendcloud`-verzendmethode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:264
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Configuration` tab, in "
"the :guilabel:`OPTIONS` section, choose the kind of shipments the shipping "
"rules apply to, via the :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud shipping rules` field."
msgstr ""
"Kies onder het tabblad :guilabel:`Sendcloud-configuratie` in de sectie "
":guilabel:`OPTIES` het type zendingen waarop de verzendregels van toepassing "
"zijn, via het veld :guilabel:`Sendcloud-verzendregels gebruiken`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:268
msgid ""
"From here, choose either: :guilabel:`Shipping` to "
"customers, :guilabel:`Returns` from customers, or :guilabel:`Both`."
msgstr ""
"Kies hier: :guilabel:`Verzending` naar klanten, :guilabel:`Retourzendingen` "
"van klanten, of :guilabel:`Beide`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Use Shipping Rules field."
msgstr "Veld Verzendregels gebruiken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:275
msgid ""
"Then, in the Sendcloud website, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Shipping rules`. Create a new shipping rule by clicking :guilabel:`Create "
"New`."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer vervolgens in de Sendcloud-website naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen --> Verzendregels`. Maak een nieuwe "
"verzendregel aan door te klikken op :guilabel:`Nieuwe aanmaken`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:278
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Actions` section, set a :guilabel:`Condition` to determine "
"when the rule applies. Then, configure what to do when packages meet the "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"Stel in de sectie :guilabel:`Acties` een :guilabel:`Voorwaarde` in om te "
"bepalen wanneer de regel van toepassing is. Configureer vervolgens wat er "
"moet gebeuren wanneer pakketten aan de voorwaarde voldoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:282
msgid ""
"`Create shipping rules on Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Maak verzendregels aan op Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:289
msgid "Shipment is too heavy"
msgstr "Zending is te zwaar"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:291
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the Sendcloud service that is configured, "
"then the weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products will need "
"to be put in different :guilabel:`Packages` to :guilabel:`Validate` the "
"transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Als de zending te zwaar is voor de geconfigureerde Sendcloud-service, wordt "
"het gewicht gesplitst om meerdere pakketten te simuleren. Producten moeten "
"in verschillende :guilabel:`Pakketten` worden geplaatst om de transfer te "
":guilabel:`valideren` en labels te genereren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rules` can also be set up in Sendcloud to use other shipping "
"methods when the weight is too heavy. However, note that these rules will "
"not apply to the shipping price calculation on the calculation on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Regels` kunnen ook worden ingesteld in Sendcloud om andere "
"verzendmethoden te gebruiken wanneer het gewicht te zwaar is. Let echter op "
"dat deze regels niet van toepassing zijn op de berekening van de "
"verzendprijs op de verkooporder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:300
msgid "Personal carrier contract"
msgstr "Persoonlijk vervoerderscontract"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:302
msgid ""
"Use custom prices from a direct carrier contract, via CSV upload, by first "
"logging into Sendcloud, navigating to :menuselection:`Settings --> Carriers "
"--> My contracts`, and then selecting the intended contract."
msgstr ""
"Gebruik aangepaste prijzen uit een direct vervoerderscontract via CSV-upload "
"door eerst in te loggen bij Sendcloud, te navigeren naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen --> Vervoerders --> Mijn contracten` en "
"vervolgens het beoogde contract te selecteren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Navigate to the contracts section in Sendcloud."
msgstr "Navigeer naar de contractensectie in Sendcloud."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:310
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contract prices` section, click :guilabel:`Download "
"CSV` and fill out the contract prices in the :guilabel:`price` column of the "
"CSV file template."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder het gedeelte :guilabel:`Contractprijzen` op :guilabel:`CSV "
"downloaden` en vul de contractprijzen in de kolom :guilabel:`prijs` van het "
"CSV-bestandssjabloon in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:314
msgid ""
"Ensure the CSV file includes the correct prices to avoid any inaccuracies."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat het CSV-bestand de juiste prijzen bevat om onnauwkeurigheden "
"te voorkomen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Show sample contract CSV from Sendcloud, highlighting the price column."
msgstr ""
"Toon voorbeeld-contract-CSV van Sendcloud, waarbij de prijskolom wordt "
"gemarkeerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:320
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload` the completed CSV file to Sendcloud, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save these prices`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Upload` het voltooide CSV-bestand naar Sendcloud en klik "
"vervolgens op :guilabel:`Deze prijzen opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:323
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to upload contract prices with carriers <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud: Hoe contractprijzen met vervoerders te uploaden <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:329
msgid ""
"Many carriers have several measures for weight. There is the actual weight "
"of the products in the parcel, and there is the *volumetric weight* "
"(:dfn:`Volumetric weight is the volume that a package occupies when in "
"transit. In other words it is the physical size of a package`)."
msgstr ""
"Veel vervoerders hanteren verschillende maten voor gewicht. Er is het "
"werkelijke gewicht van de producten in het pakket, en er is het "
"*volumetrische gewicht* (:dfn:`Volumetrisch gewicht is het volume dat een "
"pakket inneemt tijdens het transport. Met andere woorden, het is de fysieke "
"grootte van een pakket`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:334
msgid ""
"Check to see if selected carrier(s) already have defined formulas to compute "
"the volumetric weight."
msgstr ""
"Controleer of geselecteerde vervoerder(s) al gedefinieerde formules hebben "
"om het volumetrische gewicht te berekenen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:338
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to calculate & automate parcel volumetric weight <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-How-to-calculate-"
"automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud: Hoe volumetrisch gewicht van pakket te berekenen en "
"automatiseren <https://support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-"
"How-to-calculate-automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:342
msgid "Unable to calculate shipping rate"
msgstr "Kan verzendtarief niet berekenen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:344
msgid ""
"First, verify that the product being shipped has a weight that is supported "
"by the selected shipping method. If this is set, then verify that the "
"destination country (from the customer address) is supported by the carrier. "
"The country of origin (warehouse address) should also be supported by the "
"carrier."
msgstr ""
"Controleer eerst of het product dat wordt verzonden een gewicht heeft dat "
"wordt ondersteund door de geselecteerde verzendmethode. Als dit is "
"ingesteld, controleer dan of het bestemmingsland (uit het klantadres) wordt "
"ondersteund door de vervoerder. Het land van herkomst (magazijnadres) moet "
"ook worden ondersteund door de vervoerder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Starshipit shipping"
msgstr "Starshipit vervoerder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Starshipit is a shipping service operator that facilitates the integration "
"of Australasian shipping couriers with Odoo. Once integrated, users can "
"create shipping methods that will automatically get rates from specific "
"couriers (such as Australia Post, NZ Post, DHL,...) based on predefined "
"conditions."
msgstr ""
"Starshipit is een verzendserviceoperator die de integratie van "
"Australaziatische verzendvervoerders met Odoo vergemakkelijkt. Eenmaal "
"geïntegreerd kunnen gebruikers verzendmethoden aanmaken die automatisch "
"tarieven ophalen van specifieke vervoerders (zoals Australia Post, NZ Post, "
"DHL,...) op basis van vooraf gedefinieerde voorwaarden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:11
