#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:167
msgid "Production environment"
msgstr "Productieomgeving"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:169
msgid ""
"With the delivery method details configured, click the :guilabel:`Test "
"Environment` smart button to set it to :guilabel:`Production Environment`."
msgstr ""
"Klik met de geconfigureerde leveringsmethodedetails op de slimme knop "
":guilabel:`Testomgeving` om deze in te stellen op "
":guilabel:`Productieomgeving`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:173
msgid ""
"Setting the delivery method to :guilabel:`Production` creates **real** "
"shipping labels, and users are at risk of being charged through their "
"carrier account (e.g. UPS, FedEx, etc.) **before** users charge customers "
"for shipping. Verify all configurations are correct before launching the "
"delivery method to :guilabel:`Production`."
msgstr ""
"Instellen van de leveringsmethode op :guilabel:`Productie` maakt **echte** "
"verzendlabels aan en gebruikers lopen het risico via hun vervoerdersrekening "
"(bv. UPS, FedEx, enz.) te worden belast **voordat** gebruikers klanten "
"aanrekenen voor verzending. Controleer of alle configuraties correct zijn "
"voordat je de leveringsmethode op :guilabel:`Productie` lanceert."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"Test Environment\" smart button."
msgstr "Toon de slimme knop \"Testomgeving\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:187
msgid ""
"Ensure the warehouse's :guilabel:`Address` (including ZIP code) "
"and :guilabel:`Phone` number are entered accurately. To do that, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, and "
"select the desired warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat het :guilabel:`Adres` van het magazijn (inclusief postcode) "
"en :guilabel:`Telefoonnummer` nauwkeurig zijn ingevoerd. Ga hiervoor naar "
":menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Configuratie --> Magazijnen` en selecteer "
"het gewenste magazijn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:191
msgid ""
"On the warehouse configuration page, open the warehouse contact page by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Company` field."
msgstr ""
"Open op de magazijnconfiguratiepagina de magazijncontactpagina door op het "
"veld :guilabel:`Bedrijf` te klikken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Highlight the \"Company\" field."
msgstr "Markeer het veld \"Bedrijf\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:198
msgid ""
"Verify that the :guilabel:`Address` and :guilabel:`Phone` number are "
"correct, as they are required for the shipping connector to work properly."
msgstr ""
"Controleer of het :guilabel:`Adres` en :guilabel:`Telefoonnummer` correct "
"zijn, aangezien deze vereist zijn om de verzendconnector goed te laten "
"werken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show company address and phone number."
msgstr "Toon bedrijfsadres en telefoonnummer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:208
msgid "Product weight"
msgstr "Productgewicht"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:210
msgid ""
"For the carrier integration to work properly, specify the weight of products "
"by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Products`, and "
"selecting the desired product."
msgstr ""
"Specificeer voor een goede werking van de vervoerdersintegratie het gewicht "
"van producten door naar :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> Producten --> "
"Producten` te gaan en het gewenste product te selecteren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:213
msgid ""
"Then, switch to the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, and define "
"the :guilabel:`Weight` of the product in the :guilabel:`Logistics` section."
msgstr ""
"Schakel vervolgens over naar het tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad` en definieer "
"het :guilabel:`Gewicht` van het product in de sectie :guilabel:`Logistiek`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Display the \"Weight\" field in the Inventory tab of the product form."
msgstr ""
"Toon het veld \"Gewicht\" op het tabblad Voorraad van het productformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:223
msgid "Apply third-party shipping carrier"
msgstr "Vervoerder van derde partij toepassen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:225
msgid ""
"Shipping carriers can be applied on a :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, invoice, or "
"delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Vervoerders kunnen worden toegepast op een :abbr:`SO (Verkooporder)`, "
"verkoopfactuur of leveringsorder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:227
msgid ""
"After configuring the third-party carrier's :ref:`delivery method <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>` in Odoo, create or navigate "
"to a quotation by going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> "
"Quotations`."
msgstr ""
"Configureer eerst de :ref:`leveringsmethode <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-delivery-method>` van de vervoerder van de derde partij in Odoo en "
"maak vervolgens een offerte aan of navigeer ernaar via "
":menuselection:`Verkoop-app --> Orders --> Offertes`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:234
msgid "Sales order"
msgstr "Verkooporder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:236
msgid ""
"To assign a third-party shipping carrier, and get an estimated cost of "
"shipping, begin by going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> "
"Quotations`. Create or select an existing quotation, and add the cost of "
"shipping through a third-party carrier to a quotation, by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Add Shipping` button in the bottom-right corner of "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Verkoop-app --> Orders --> Offertes` om een "
"vervoerder van een derde partij toe te wijzen en een geschatte verzendkosten "
"te verkrijgen. Maak een offerte aan of selecteer een bestaande offerte en "
"voeg de verzendkosten via een vervoerder van een derde partij toe aan de "
"offerte door op de knop :guilabel:`Verzending toevoegen` rechtsonder in het "
"tabblad :guilabel:`Orderregels` te klikken."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"Add shipping\" button at the bottom of a quotation."
msgstr "Toon de knop \"Verzending toevoegen\" onderaan een offerte."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:245
msgid ""
"In the resulting :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window, select the "
"intended carrier from the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` drop-down menu. "
"The :guilabel:`Cost` field is automatically filled based on:"
msgstr ""
"Selecteer in het pop-upvenster :guilabel:`Een verzendmethode toevoegen` de "
"gewenste vervoerder in het vervolgkeuzemenu :guilabel:`Verzendmethode`. Het "
"veld :guilabel:`Kosten` wordt automatisch ingevuld op basis van:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:249
msgid ""
"the amount specified in the :guilabel:`Total Order Weight` field (if it is "
"not provided, the sum of :ref:`product weights <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-weight>` in the order is used)"
msgstr ""
"het bedrag opgegeven in het veld :guilabel:`Totaal ordergewicht` (als dit "
"niet is opgegeven, wordt de som van de :ref:`productgewichten <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` in de order gebruikt)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:251
msgid ""
"the distance between the warehouse's :ref:`source address <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` and the customer's address."
msgstr ""
"de afstand tussen het :ref:`bronadres <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-source-address>` van het magazijn en het adres van de klant."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:256
msgid ""
"After selecting a third-party provider in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` "
"field, click :guilabel:`Get Rate` in the :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` "
"pop-up window to get the estimated cost through the shipping connector. "
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Add` button to add the delivery charge to the |"
"SO| or invoice."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer een provider van een derde partij in het veld "
":guilabel:`Verzendmethode` en klik op :guilabel:`Tarief ophalen` in het pop-"
"upvenster :guilabel:`Een verzendmethode toevoegen` om de geschatte kosten "
"via de verzendconnector op te halen. Klik vervolgens op de knop "
":guilabel:`Toevoegen` om de verzendkosten toe te voegen aan de |SO| of "
"factuur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:262
msgid ":doc:`Charge customers for shipping after product delivery <invoicing>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Klanten laten betalen voor verzending na levering van het product "
"<invoicing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:269
msgid ""
"For users making shipments without installing the *Sales* app, assign the "
"shipping carrier to the delivery order, by first going to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory` app. Then, from the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Overview` dashboard, select the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` operation type, "
"and choose the desired delivery order that is not already marked "
"as :guilabel:`Done` or :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikers die zendingen maken zonder de *Verkoop*-app te installeren, "
"kunnen de vervoerder toewijzen aan de leveringsorder door eerst naar de "
":menuselection:`Voorraad`-app te gaan. Selecteer vervolgens vanaf het "
":guilabel:`Voorraadoverzicht`-dashboard het bewerkingstype "
":guilabel:`Leveringsorders` en kies de gewenste leveringsorder die nog niet "
"is gemarkeerd als :guilabel:`Voltooid` of :guilabel:`Geannuleerd`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:275
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Additional info` tab, set the :guilabel:`Carrier` field to "
"the desired third-party shipping carrier. When the delivery method is set "
"to :ref:`production mode <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>`, a :guilabel:`Tracking Reference` is provided."
msgstr ""
"Stel in het tabblad :guilabel:`Extra informatie` het veld "
":guilabel:`Vervoerder` in op de gewenste vervoerder van een derde partij. "
"Wanneer de leveringsmethode is ingesteld op :ref:`productiemodus <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>`, wordt een "
":guilabel:`Trackingreferentie` verstrekt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:281
msgid ":doc:`Generate shipping labels <labels>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Verzendlabels genereren <labels>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the delivery order's \"Additional info\" tab."
msgstr "Toon het tabblad \"Extra informatie\" van de leveringsorder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:290
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Problemen oplossen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:292
msgid ""
"Since shipping connectors can sometimes be complex to set up, here are some "
"checks to try when things are not working as expected:"
msgstr ""
"Omdat verzendconnectors soms complex kunnen zijn om in te stellen, zijn hier "
"enkele controles om te proberen wanneer dingen niet werken zoals verwacht:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:295
msgid ""
"Ensure the :ref:`warehouse information <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-source-address>` (e.g., address and phone number) in Odoo is "
"correct **and** matches the records saved in the shipping provider's website."
msgstr ""
"Controleer of de :ref:`magazijninformatie <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-source-address>` (bv. adres en telefoonnummer) in Odoo correct is "
"**en** overeenkomt met de gegevens die zijn opgeslagen op de website van de "
"verzendprovider."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:298
msgid ""
"Verify that the :ref:`package type <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-"
"type>` and parameters are valid for the shipping carrier. To check, ensure "
"the shipment can be directly created on the shipping carrier's website."
msgstr ""
"Controleer of het :ref:`pakkettype <inventory/warehouses_storage/package-"
"type>` en de parameters geldig zijn voor de vervoerder. Controleer dit door "
"te verifiëren dat de zending direct kan worden aangemaakt op de website van "
"de vervoerder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:301
msgid ""
"When encountering a price mismatch between Odoo's estimated cost and the "
"provider's charge, first ensure the delivery method is set "
"to :ref:`production environment <inventory/shipping_receiving/production-"
"env>`."
msgstr ""
"Controleer bij een prijsverschil tussen de geschatte kosten van Odoo en de "
"kosten van de provider eerst of de leveringsmethode is ingesteld op "
":ref:`productieomgeving <inventory/shipping_receiving/production-env>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:305
msgid ""
"Then, create the shipment in both the carrier's website and Odoo, and verify "
"the prices are the same across Odoo, the shipping provider, and in the "
"*debug logs*."
msgstr ""
"Maak vervolgens de zending aan op zowel de website van de vervoerder als in "
"Odoo en controleer of de prijzen hetzelfde zijn in Odoo, bij de "
"verzendprovider en in de *debug logs*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:309
msgid ""
"When checking for a price mismatch in the debug logs, if the request says "
"the package weighs six kilograms, but the response from FedEx says the "
"package weights seven kilograms, it concludes that the issue is on FedEx's "
"side."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer je in de foutopsporingslogboeken controleert op een prijsverschil en "
"het verzoek zegt dat het pakket zes kilogram weegt, maar het antwoord van "
"FedEx zegt dat het pakket zeven kilogram weegt, concludeer je dat het "
"probleem aan de kant van FedEx ligt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:314
msgid "Debug log"
msgstr "Foutopsporingslogboek"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:316
msgid ""
"Track shipping data inconsistencies by activating debug logging. To do that, "
"go to the delivery method's configuration page (:menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Configuration --> Shipping Method`), and select the desired shipping "
"method. Click the :guilabel:`No Debugging` smart button to "
"activate :guilabel:`Debug Requests`."
msgstr ""
"Volg inconsistenties in verzendgegevens door foutopsporingslogboeken te "
"activeren. Ga hiervoor naar de configuratiepagina van de leveringsmethode "
"(:menuselection:`Voorraad app --> Configuratie --> Leveringsmethode`) en "
"selecteer de gewenste leveringsmethode. Klik op de slimme knop "
":guilabel:`Geen foutopsporing` om :guilabel:`Verzoeken debuggen` te "
"activeren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"No Debug\" smart button."
msgstr "Toon de slimme knop \"Geen foutopsporing\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:325
msgid ""
"With :guilabel:`Debug Requests` activated, each time the shipping connector "
"is used to estimate the cost of shipping, records are saved in "
"the :guilabel:`Logging` report. To access the report, turn "
"on :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Database Structure section "
"--> Logging`."
msgstr ""
"Met :guilabel:`Verzoeken debuggen` geactiveerd, worden elke keer dat de "
"verzendconnector wordt gebruikt om de verzendkosten te schatten, records "
"opgeslagen in het :guilabel:`Loggen` rapport. Open het rapport door de "
":ref:`ontwikkelaarsmodus <developer-mode>` in te schakelen en ga naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen app --> Technisch --> sectie "
"Databasestructuur --> Loggen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:331
msgid ""
"Logs are created for a shipping method each time the :ref:`Get Rate "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>` button is clicked "
"on :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` and invoices, **and** when a customer adds the "
"shipping carrier to their order through the *Website* app."
msgstr ""
"Logs worden aangemaakt voor een leveringsmethode elke keer dat op de knop "
":ref:`Tarief ophalen <inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>` wordt "
"geklikt op :abbr:`SOs (verkooporders)` en verkoopfacturen, **en** wanneer "
"een klant de vervoerder toevoegt aan zijn bestelling via de *Website* app."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show how to find the \"Logging\" option from the \"Technical\" menu."
msgstr "Toon hoe je de optie \"Loggen\" vindt vanuit het menu \"Technisch\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:340
msgid ""
"Click the *HTTP request* line item to open a detailed page, and verify the "
"correct information is sent from Odoo to the shipping carrier. In the *HTTP "
"response*, verify that the same information is received."
msgstr ""
"Klik op het regelitem *HTTP-verzoek* om een gedetailleerde pagina te openen "
"en verifieer dat de juiste informatie van Odoo naar de vervoerder wordt "
"verzonden. Verifieer in het *HTTP-antwoord* dat dezelfde informatie wordt "
"ontvangen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:None
msgid "Show debug request history in Settings > Technical > Logging."
msgstr ""
"Toon foutopsporingsverzoekgeschiedenis in Instellingen > Technisch > Loggen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:3
msgid "UPS integration"
msgstr "UPS integratie"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:5
msgid ""
"UPS is a shipping carrier service that integrates with Odoo to coordinate "
"shipping to all regions. Once integrated, users can create shipping methods "
"that estimate shipping costs and :doc:`generate labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"UPS is een vervoerderservice die integreert met Odoo om verzending naar alle "
"regio's te coördineren. Eenmaal geïntegreerd kunnen gebruikers "
"leveringsmethoden aanmaken die verzendkosten schatten en :doc:`labels "
"genereren <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:12
msgid "To set up the UPS shipping connector in Odoo, complete these steps:"
msgstr "Voltooi deze stappen om de UPS verzendconnector in Odoo in te stellen:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:14
msgid ""
"Create a UPS account to get :ref:`account number <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-account-number>`"
msgstr ""
"Maak een UPS rekening aan om een :ref:`rekeningnummer <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-account-number>` te krijgen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:16
msgid ""
"Create UPS developer account to get :ref:`client credentials <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-client-id>`"
msgstr ""
"Maak een UPS ontwikkelaarsrekening aan om :ref:`clientreferenties <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/ups-client-id>` te krijgen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:18
msgid "Set up shipping method in Odoo"
msgstr "Stel de leveringsmethode in Odoo in"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:21
msgid ""
"When configuring a shipping method to use UPS, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` is set to :guilabel:`UPS`, **NOT** :guilabel:`UPS "
"Legacy`."
msgstr ""
"Zorg er bij het configureren van een leveringsmethode om UPS te gebruiken "
"voor dat de :guilabel:`provider` is ingesteld op :guilabel:`UPS`, **NIET** "
":guilabel:`UPS Legacy`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:24
msgid ""
"If shipping methods currently exist with the :guilabel:`Provider` set "
"to :guilabel:`UPS Legacy`, archive them, and create new shipping methods "
"using :guilabel:`UPS`, instead."
msgstr ""
"Als er momenteel leveringsmethoden bestaan met de :guilabel:`provider` "
"ingesteld op :guilabel:`UPS Legacy`, archiveer ze en maak nieuwe "
"leveringsmethoden aan met :guilabel:`UPS`."

