"../productivity/dashboards>`-app, stellen je in staat om kernstatistieken "
"met betrekking tot magazijnactiviteiten en -beheer, evenals voorraadbeheer, "
"te monitoren en te analyseren:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`Warehouse Daily Operations dashboard <inventory/dashboards/warehouse-"
"daily-operations-dashboard>`: monitors task completion and scheduled "
"activities"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Magazijn dagelijkse activiteiten dashboard <inventory/dashboards/"
"warehouse-daily-operations-dashboard>`: monitort taakvoltooiing en geplande "
"activiteiten"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:12
msgid ""
":ref:`Operation analysis dashboard <inventory/dashboards/operation-analysis-"
"dashboard>`: measures efficiency KPIs"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Bewerkingsanalyse dashboard <inventory/dashboards/operation-analysis-"
"dashboard>`: meet efficiëntie-KPI's"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:14
msgid ""
":ref:`Warehouse Metrics dashboard <inventory/dashboards/warehouse-metrics-"
"dashboard>`: assesses stock value and quantity"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Magazijnstatistieken dashboard <inventory/dashboards/warehouse-metrics-"
"dashboard>`: beoordeelt voorraadwaarde en -hoeveelheid"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:17
msgid ""
"To access these dashboards, go to the **Dashboards** app, then, in the left "
"panel, navigate to the :guilabel:`Logistics` section and click the name of "
"the relevant dashboard. The dashboard opens in the main view."
msgstr ""
"Om deze dashboards te openen, ga je naar de **Dashboards**-app en navigeer "
"je vervolgens in het linkerpaneel naar de sectie :guilabel:`Logistiek` en "
"klik je op de naam van het relevante dashboard. Het dashboard opent in de "
"hoofdweergave."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:22
msgid ""
"The :ref:`rights to access <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` Odoo dashboards "
"are based on user groups, and are managed within the **Dashboards** app. By "
"default, the :guilabel:`Operation analysis` and :guilabel:`Warehouse "
"Metrics` dashboards are only visible to, and can only be accessed by, users "
"with admin access to the **Inventory** app."
msgstr ""
"De :ref:`rechten voor toegang <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` tot Odoo-"
"dashboards zijn gebaseerd op gebruikersgroepen en worden beheerd binnen de "
"**Dashboards**-app. Standaard zijn het :guilabel:`Bewerkingsanalyse`- en "
":guilabel:`Magazijnstatistieken`-dashboard alleen zichtbaar voor en "
"toegankelijk voor gebruikers met beheerderstoegang tot de **Voorraad**-app."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/dashboards.rst:28
